[{"name":"主剧情挑战","key":"juqing","content":[{"name":"希卡之石的指示地","content":[{"type":"title","content":"第一章线路图"},{"type":"text","content":"在出了 复苏神庙后 在 山路上和老人对话触发 任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/604e9556ad042e686dbd9a5285f85856d43dd1eb.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"之后就可以解锁地图 同时地图会出现一个坐标 我们需要按着地图方向找到这个位置"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/0fb94656d53da82458bd0761306651598440cbeb.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"途中有个教堂一样的废墟 里面有个女神像 在后面解锁神庙后到这里可以增加血量 （也是一个回忆点）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/84010e2a04e23ea2b2166bc92b10bc33ed38c3eb.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"到做标位置 可以发现一个石洞 进去 把希卡之石 放在机关上 就可以解锁世界上的区域塔 和神庙"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a151a233ec3834bb97bb69ec8714c27bd3823de8.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/0d55dc7bd282868935127c0265f97fbd4d7c37e8.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b6f0f0f97fbd4c7cade7f7f2b8bad341027d30e8.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"激活初始之塔后 从上面爬下来 老人会飞过来 告诉你使命 需要击杀 灾厄盖侬 拯救塞尔达 同时触发新的主线 封锁的台地 需要你完成挑战 拿到滑翔伞 "},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3d002dbad341037d7f6302c5a9bc7dc5ce672de8.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/23fd63c5cf672b5f7112ce253314f4d0b40327e8.jpg"}]},{"name":"主线-访问英帕","content":[{"type":"title","content":"主线-访问英帕"},{"type":"text","content":"离开初始台地之后，在下图位置，进入【瓦希·辽科神庙】，这个神庙属于滑翔翼的基本教程。此神庙攻略：点击进入"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190718_syj_380_12/image001_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"继续向东走，前往下图的双子山之塔，点亮周围的地图。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190718_syj_380_12/image003_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"双子塔旁边有3个神庙，在北边的山有两个神庙，右边的山有一座神庙。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190718_syj_380_12/image005_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"翻过双子山，在双子哥哥桥旁边有一座神庙。"},{"type":"text","content":"哈尤·达玛神庙攻略：点击进入"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190718_syj_380_12/image007_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"通过神庙试炼之后，来到旁边的双子驿站，可以领取两个迷你挑战任务，完成后可以获得前期比较强力的武器火焰剑和坐骑。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190718_syj_380_12/image009_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"完成这两个挑战之后，就可以骑马赶路了，我们接下来就要前往卡卡利科村，顺着大陆走，在下面地图位置可以触发一个迷你挑战，这个挑战前期务必完成，可以增加背包容量。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190718_syj_380_12/image011_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"来到卡卡利科村，与英帕交谈，得知林克失去了记忆，如果想要拯救塞尔达，就要解放四神兽，但是目前的实力还不允许，我们需要前往哈特诺古代研究所所长升级希卡之石。接下来就要去拜访所长。在卡卡利科村可以购买潜行服装，如果有钱了一定要买下来。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190718_syj_380_12/image013_S.jpg"}]},{"name":"主线-塞尔达的路标","content":[{"type":"title","content":"主线-塞尔达的路标"},{"type":"text","content":"此时传送到双子驿站骑马前往哈特诺村，这里的路上会遇到商人将我们拦下，并且变身忍者攻击，一定要注意安全。接着到下图的哈塔诺之塔处开启地图。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190719_lc_475_22/image001_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"高塔上有荆棘，要按下图箭头路线向上爬。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190719_lc_475_22/image003_S.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190719_lc_475_22/image005_S.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190719_lc_475_22/image007_S.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190719_lc_475_22/image009_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"点亮之后来到哈特诺村，村边上有一个神庙。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190719_lc_475_22/image011_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"接着顺着路向山上走，到了哈特诺古代研究所。得知希卡之石缺少照相功能。需要所长帮我们修复，但是因为没有能力，需要我们去古代炉采火。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190719_lc_475_22/image013_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"这里拿着火把去就行，注意一点一定要看右下角天气有没有雨，有雨的话就再篝火处调整时间。在取了火之后，往回走，这里沿着道路走，路边的灯靠近就可以点亮蓝火，如果火灭了也能直接在路灯处取火继续前进。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190719_lc_475_22/image015_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"修复好照相功能后，对着所长拍张照就可以离开了。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190719_lc_475_22/image017_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"通过传送返回英帕身边，她告诉我们如果想要找到以前的记忆就要找到照片的地点唤起回忆。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190719_lc_475_22/image019_S.jpg"}]},{"name":"主线-寻找精灵之泉","content":[{"type":"title","content":"主线-寻找精灵之泉"},{"type":"text","content":"离开英帕的屋子，在村外找到康吉斯，对话后得知他要去寻找精灵之泉。跟随他一直向前走。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190719_lc_475_22/image021_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"到了半山腰他就会抱怨累了步向前走，我们只好自己向前继续前进。顺着路向前走就能看到一个巨大的花。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190719_lc_475_22/image023_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"给予花100卢比，大精灵就会出现，我们就可以强化防具了。目前能强化的是海利亚套装、海利亚士兵套装以及潜行套装，需要的材料都比较好获得，建议把这9件装备强化。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190719_lc_475_22/image025_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"强化完毕后，使用照相机对着精灵之泉拍张照，旁边的精灵能够在死亡时满血复活，穿着潜行套装过去很容易抓到。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190719_lc_475_22/image027_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"返回刚刚康吉斯休息的地方，把照片交给他，任务完成，同时他会告诉我们关于照片位置的信息。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190719_lc_475_22/image029_S.jpg"}]},{"name":"主线-勇者之剑","content":[{"type":"title","content":"主线-勇者之剑"},{"type":"text","content":"在生命值到达13颗心的时候，就可以去拿大师之剑了。首先通过传送来到森林之塔，位置在下图标记，之后使用滑翔伞向北飞，来到海拉鲁大森林的南面入口，这里不能直接飞到森林内部，即使飞进去也会被传送出来。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190723_syj_380_9/image005_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"进入森林后，先用火把点燃台子，然后沿着火焰向内部前进。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190723_syj_380_9/image007_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"到达下图的两个火堆的位置，拾取地上的火把，顺着周围萤火的飘的方向前进。这里走一段停一段观察，如果一直走的话，因为你速度比萤火快，所以容易判断错误方向，判断方向的时候一定要原地不动的判断。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190723_syj_380_9/image009_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"到了峡谷处，一直向前走，进走出迷宫，进入森林内部了。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190723_syj_380_9/image011_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"进入内部后，一直向前走，就可以看到大师之剑，触发剧情，剧情结束后，就可以拔剑了，只有在13颗心以上才能拔出，否则就死亡。这把剑就可以一直使用了，因为没有耐久之后等待10分钟就可以修复，满心的时候可以投掷出一道剑气，心心越多剑气越远，对抗盖侬和守护者时两倍伤害。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190723_syj_380_9/image013_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"拔出剑即可完成任务，在这里有道具店，和之前给我们背包扩容的NPC，这里如果有更多的“呀哈哈”可以找他扩容背包。只要传送离开森林，如果有DLC就会触发剑之试炼任务，可以将剑的攻击力由30增加到60。在获得英杰之服和大师之剑后，就可以去解放四神兽了。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190723_syj_380_9/image015_S.jpg"}]},{"name":"主线-水神兽","content":[{"type":"title","content":"主线-水神兽"},{"type":"text","content":"千辛万苦走到卓拉领地"},{"type":"text","content":"来到达尔布尔桥，会遇到卓拉王子，他告诉我们因为现在下雨，无法攀爬，只能跑到卓拉领地，并且给予我们一些防雷的药。接下来的路推荐大家穿着潜行衣前进，减少不必要的战斗。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image001_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"到了山脚下希多会叫住我们，并告诉我们前面的路更加危险，但我们还是需要继续前进。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image003_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"到达下图位置时希多还会和我们打招呼，这时不要过河，而是从右边的小路前进。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image005_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"小路中有电蝙蝠，要趁它们还没发现我们的时候用弓箭射下来，就是墙上黄色的就是。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image007_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"通过之后按照下图路线蹲着向前走，否则被蜥蜴发现就会很麻烦。到了桥上之后就已经完成一半的路程了，我们要继续前进。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image009_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"向前走不远处有一个石头挡住去路，用静止器把他挪开。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image011_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"一路躲避怪物的攻击来到拉鲁特大桥，希多和我们打完招呼后，会有敌人来袭击，使用大师剑可以很轻松的将其打败。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image013_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"继续前进就可以来到卓拉领地了，来到领地后，首先进入奈兹·耀玛神庙。神庙攻略：点击进入"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image015_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"通过神庙试炼后，去上层与族长对话，如果想要打败水神兽就需要电箭，并给予我们卓拉铠甲，有了这个铠甲就可以顺着瀑布向上走了（记住是顺着瀑布的水，而不是瀑布旁边没有水的墙）。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image017_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"如果电箭够就不用去雷兽山了，如果不够就要去，到了雷兽山可是拾取电箭，基本上都插在树上，然后山顶有一个半人马怪，如果对自己的操作没信心就不要招惹了，直接跑就行，如果有信心就和他刚正面。"},{"type":"text","content":"半人马莱尼尔打法：近身三连斩的时候，我们不停用后跳，只要躲开第一下，后面两下必定有一次能进入林克时间；远距离喷火，因为他蓄力时间过长，我们需要用弓箭进行打断；在他头顶上攻击他的头部，他会进入大硬直，这是可以骑在他身上进行输出；不要离开莱尼尔的视野，否则他释放的从天而降的雷箭很难躲。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image019_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"水之神兽瓦·露塔"},{"type":"text","content":"获得足够多的电箭后，就可以去讨伐水神兽了，打水神兽时，我们是骑在希多的背上，无法控制方向。BOSS的攻击方法有两种：1、冰方块，是要用弓箭把射一下就可以了，因为方块是向前飘的，只要瞄准方块右边一点，基本上都能射下来；2、水雷，水雷会来到我们后方，比冰块还好防，只要对着屁股射箭就行了，这里射箭用普通弓箭即可。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image021_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"每当下几波进攻，希多会带我们到瀑布下方，冲上去打开滑翔伞，瞄准进入林克时间，换上电箭，射下图红色的点即可，一共有四个，每次打一个，全部打完就OK了！"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image023_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"进入神兽内部，第一层后两个眼睛，一个小型守护者，第一个眼睛在门口，第二个眼睛在水里，都破坏之后，使用制冰器把门抬起来，获得水神兽地图。获得地图后，在旁边的水里可以用磁铁拉上来一个宝箱。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image025_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第一个终端：就在刚刚获得地图的位置对面，转身就能看到，用磁铁顺时针摇动齿轮，就能解锁第一个终端了。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image027_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第二个终端：从旁边进入二层，击败门口的小型守护者后，终端机就在齿轮里，等终端机露出水面后，把出水口冻上，进行解锁。可以从外侧踩着齿轮到出水口上方，可以看到一个宝箱，打开获得100卢比。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image029_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"从旁边击破一个眼睛到达第三层，进入齿轮前。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image031_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第三个终端：打开地图，将大象鼻子调到从上向下数第三个位置。站在下面的台子上，在球到下图位置，把他定住，这样等终端转上来，我们就可以进去解锁第三个终端了。在齿轮里还有一个宝箱，同样适用静止器将取出。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image033_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"在齿轮外侧还有一个宝箱，宝箱上有一个眼睛，需要在看到宝箱后把象鼻子调到从上向下第五个位置，用弓箭射眼睛，在去捡宝箱。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image035_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"解锁第三个终端后，从齿轮外侧上到四层，上面有一个小型守护者，将守护者击杀后踩左边的机关放下瀑布，接下来就可以通过瀑布直接飞上来了。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image037_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第四个终端：把象鼻子调到最下面的档位，从下图位置利用滑翔翼跳到象鼻尖上。把象鼻子调到从上向下第三个档位，有第四个终端，解锁，不要急着解锁第五个，在鼻子上去的宝箱。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image039_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"站在第四个终端解锁的位置向下看，可以看到一个方形小口，利用滑翔翼跳进去。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image041_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第五个终端：下来之后，把眼镜打掉，然后用磁铁转动墙上的齿轮，把天花板打开。接着把鼻子调到从上向下第五个档位，就会浇灭下面的火，下去就可以解锁了。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image043_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"解锁完五个终端，回到出口处，准备最终BOSS战。"},{"type":"text","content":"BOSS战打法：第一阶段，使用弓箭攻击BOSS的眼睛，然后近战用大师剑攻击，他的长矛攻击是可以闪避躲开的，打到半血进入第二阶段；第二阶段，我们只能站在四个台子上战斗，这里他会向我们扔冰块，只要使用制冰器制作掩体挡住即可，输出的话就全靠电箭射眼睛了，反复几次就能将其击败。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image045_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"战胜BOSS后，拾取一个心之容器，触发剧情，米法将自己的治愈能力教给林克，林克获得能力：迎接米法的祈福。剧情结束后，回到卓拉领地，在族长旁边的宝箱内获得米法的武器【光麟之枪】。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/07/20190724_syj_380_17/image047_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"至此，解放水神兽任务完成。"}]},{"name":"主线-雷神兽","content":[{"type":"title","content":"主线-雷神兽"},{"type":"text","content":"潜入！男子禁入的小镇"},{"type":"text","content":"在地图左下角的古科·齐塞神庙旁边与本杰明对话，接取任务。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image001_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"接下来往回走前往卡拉卡拉集市，爬到集市最高的建筑上，花600卢比购买淑女装（耐热，在沙漠地区不掉血）。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image003_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"穿上淑女装之后，传送回古科·齐塞神庙，进入城内，与璐菊对话。璐菊让我们去夺回雷鸣头盔。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image005_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"对话结束后，到村东边的位置花20卢比租一个沙海象。骑着沙海象前往目标地点，在半路上会有落石，注意躲避。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image007_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"下了海象车之后，一路向目标地点跑，不要停，路上的忍者会袭击我们，但是追不上，到了目标地点，击败追上来的即可。接下来有七个门，用火把依次烧开挡在门前的布就能通过了。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image009_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"到了伊盖队基地内换上潜行装，先在下图位置拿到香蕉，然后看下面的敌人向左走之后，快速通过。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image011_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"下一个站在门口的敌人，只要让他看我们一眼，头上出现问号，就赶紧藏起来，如果出现感叹号被发现就会出现大量敌人，并且对方砍我们一刀就会死去。接着到达下图位置，爬左边的楼梯可以上楼，楼上可以拾取大量香蕉，香蕉可以用来吸引敌人的注意力。拾取后回到下图位置向右走。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image013_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"我们要去往红圈处的梯子出，路上一共有两个敌人，只要用香蕉把他们吸引住，就能顺利爬上梯子。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image015_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"到了上方之后，直接来到门口，把下面的敌人吸引走之后，进门就可以了。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image017_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"进入没人看守的房间可以用磁力抓取器获得地上的宝箱，然后拉开旁边的门，进入BOSS战。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image019_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"可盖大人打法：第一阶段，等他举起石球的时候，身上护盾消失，直接使用弓箭打他一下，他就会被球砸到，我们上前输出，反复几次就会进入第二阶段；"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image021_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第二阶段，他会飞到中央使用两个球，这回的射箭时机是其中一个球到他的头顶，就可以射他了，他会被球砸到我们身边，连续输出进入第三阶段。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image023_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第三阶段是最简单的一个阶段，我们只需拿出磁力抓取器，等着他举起铁球，举起来的瞬间，抓取，松手，他就会被砸到我们身边了，用不了几次就能将其击杀。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image025_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"战斗结束后，获得雷鸣头盔，我们将其送还给璐菊。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image027_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"雷之神兽瓦·娜波力斯"},{"type":"text","content":"在王宫二楼与女王对话，她说让我们骑沙海象前往监视台。同样，我们花20卢比租一个海象前往监视台。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image029_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"在屋子里可以获得格鲁德之弓，并且免费睡觉补血，休整完毕后，通过左边的梯子爬到上方与璐菊对话，决定讨伐雷神兽。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image031_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"雷神兽攻略：首先我们是骑着沙海象战斗，只要一直在璐菊的保护罩内就不会被雷攻击到。在战斗中我们使用两连发的弓+爆炸箭，一次就可以打爆一条腿，一共四条，如果站在海象上不好射击，就下来攻击，雷神兽速度很慢，速度快的话很快就能战胜，战胜之后，就可以进入内部。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image033_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"进入神兽每部，杀掉第一个守护者。进入开始旋转靠近头部的机关，看到终端之后，站在下图位置，旋转几次就能跳过去解锁了。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image035_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第二个终端：首先站在我们进入内部的这个洞口处，开始转动靠近头部的机关，让我们所站的位置进行转动。转到最上面，来到外部。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image037_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"就是下图洞口位置出去。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image039_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"到了外面会看到一个十字转动机关，顺时针转控制左边的灯，逆时针转控制右边的灯，通过转动让两个灯都亮起来。会出现升降梯，坐升降梯到上面就可以发现第二个终端。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image041_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第三个终端：通过靠近尾部的机关，来到右后腿的外侧。再转动靠近尾部的机关，直到看到终端，进入内部，转动机关，注入机关。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image043_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第四、五个终端：来到神兽尾部，拥有四个滑动杆的位置，让他们通过电线联通道尾部。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image045_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"之后站在下图位置，转动神兽内的机关，让每个机关的线都在上方，这样就会触发机关。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image047_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"上来之后，把面前的眼睛打了，进入内部后把所有能打的眼睛都打了。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image049_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"接着坐升降梯向下，在过程中会看到一个金属宝箱，对面还有一个发电球，拿着发电球到最下方。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image051_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"从最上层，直接跳到对面。对面也有升降梯，可以获得第二个发电球和一个终端。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image053_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"在两个发电球中间区域，有小型守护者守卫的房间，把两个发电球都带到房间内，分别放在下图位置的两侧，就可以解锁最后一个终端了。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image055_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"回到神兽中间位置，把终端装置移动下来，调查总控制台，进入BOSS战。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image057_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"雷咒盖侬打法：第一阶段，他放雷球的时候，我们不停的跑动就不会被命中；在他瞬移攻击的时候，我们只要按住防御键就可以挡住，然后造成BOSS大量硬直，接下来连续输出就能造成大量伤害，反复几次就可以打到他第二阶段。"},{"type":"text","content":"第二阶段，BOSS会往地上插铁柱，我们用磁力抓取器将铁柱抓起来，靠近BOSS，就会有雷劈BOSS，把他打到地上之后和第一阶段就相同了，连续输出，击败BOSS完成任务。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image059_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"击败BOSS后，乌尔波扎出现，并交给林克【英杰乌尔波扎的愤怒】，可以长按Y蓄力让周围发动雷电。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image061_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"接着去找璐菊完成任务，她身后有两个宝箱，是这次任务的奖励，旁边的雷鸣头盔则需要完成迷你挑战获得"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_4/image063_S.jpg"}]},{"name":"主线-风神兽","content":[{"type":"title","content":"主线-风神兽 风之神兽瓦·梅德"},{"type":"text","content":"首先来到利特村，一直向上爬，与村长卡昂对话。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_11/image001_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"接着向下走，就能遇到莎琪，对话结束后，不要急着去找特巴，而是在村内购买一套防寒服，价格很贵，所以如果没钱的话就去赚点钱。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_11/image003_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"来到特巴所在的训练场之后，准备开始训练，训练项目是3分钟打5个靶子，难度非常低，只要在天上按射箭就会进入慢动作，靶子非常多，慢慢瞄就行，不用担心体力不够，就算垂直下落也能完成。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_11/image005_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"完成后就要进行BOSS战了，本场战斗难度并不高，利用滑翔伞进行移动，接着在空中进行射击，使用爆炸箭攻击四个角的炮台，两发就能打爆一个，全部打爆之后，进入神兽内部。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_11/image007_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"进入神兽内，先打掉我们眼前的眼睛。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_11/image009_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"接下来就要去对面，下面的铁质方块都是可以移动，搭上一条路，就可以到对面，击杀一个小型守护者，就可以解锁地图了。解锁地图后，回到下图位置，通过上升气流到左边的宝箱处，打掉眼睛，到左边的房间里。下面有两层，各有一个宝箱，各位玩家可以去拾取。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_11/image011_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"到了左边的房间后，先打掉终端前面的眼睛。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_11/image013_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"接着攻击下图黄色的灯。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_11/image015_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"我们从靠窗的斜坡到上层，利用气流到第一个终端。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_11/image017_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"接着在下图的位置，丢进去一个圆形炸弹，就可以炸开石头。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_11/image019_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"从窗户外围利用滑翔伞飞进另一间屋内。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_11/image021_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"解锁终端之后，炸开终端旁边的石墙，取出铁球，利用静止器加攻击，让铁球撞击墙上凸起的机关，打开房间正门，离开房间。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_11/image023_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"对面下图右侧的房间，可以通过地图调整神兽倾斜的角度。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_11/image011_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"首先砍下面的灯，然后清理掉房间内的眼睛。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_11/image025_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"把上方的类似风车的东西移动到左边，让两个风车都转起来，这样下面的门会打开。使用静止器将轨道上的物体撞击右边的开关，就可以解锁第三个终端。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_11/image027_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"来到神兽最下层，利用倾斜的高低差，进入最后两个终端（左右各一个）。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_11/image029_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"全部终端解锁后，来到神兽最上方，准备BOSS战。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_11/image031_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"风咒盖侬打法：第一阶段，不听的移动，他的激光炮只要我们在移动就打不到我们，龙卷风就要跑来一点，他的弱点是头部，只要攻击他的头部，把他打到地上，再进行输出，就可以了。"},{"type":"text","content":"第二阶段，在BOSS半血后会进入第二阶段，增加4个发激光的小怪，只要围着中央的控制台走，就能躲开大部分攻击，我们的还手方式和第一阶段一样，也可以利用左右两侧的上升气流在空中攻击，这样有林克时间，能够射的更准。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_11/image033_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"在BOSS打完后，可以获得【英杰力巴尔的勇猛】，长按X不放，可以产生一道向上的气流，这招可以用在很多地方，非常实用，接下来返回利特村，与村长对话，完成任务，村长旁边的宝箱内有【大鹫弓】是任务奖励。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190827_syj_380_11/image035_S.jpg"}]},{"name":"主线-火神兽","content":[{"type":"title","content":"主线-火神兽"},{"type":"text","content":"获得抗火服"},{"type":"text","content":"首先来到山麓驿站，在下图位置，在驿站中可以购买防火药水。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image001_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"服用放火药水后，来到【南部采矿场】，然后把时间调到晚上，就可以看到一个NPC，领取迷你挑战，换上潜行装，抓10个抗火蜥，交给他，就能获得【耐火石铠】。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image003_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"接着就沿着大路一直前往鼓隆城，路上会遇到火神兽爆发，这里只要躲在不露天的位置躲避即可。来到城内，在商店购买耐火套装。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image005_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"解救阿陨"},{"type":"text","content":"在村子里根据地图指示找到布尔多，他让我们帮忙救出阿陨。顺着布尔多指的方向上山。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image007_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"来到目标地点后，就是去救阿陨，路上的敌人只要用冰箭都可以一箭秒杀，所以难度不高。炮台的用法就是向炮筒里扔进去一个炸弹，利用摇杆操作方向，只有两个档位，引爆炸弹发射炮弹。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image009_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"最后阿陨所在的洞口被挡住，要利用下图的炮台将石头打破，因为炮台只有两个档位，所以一定要在移动的过程中，开炮，多试几次就可以打掉了。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image011_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"救下阿陨后回去报告，接下来，去火神兽附近，这里阿陨被两名敌人包围，将其消灭救下阿陨。接着让阿陨充当炮弹把大桥放下。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image013_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"入侵火神兽"},{"type":"text","content":"通过桥之后火神兽会放出侦察机，主角和阿陨都不能被发现，否则会降下火球把我们砸死。我们可以自由行动，在阿陨附近按十字键↓吹口哨让阿陨原地不动或者跟随我们。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image015_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第一个侦察机，我们和阿陨一起躲在红圈处，等侦察机过去我们直接向前走即可。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image017_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第二个侦察机，让阿陨原地不动，我们爬上左边的峭壁，在上面有两块石头，推下去就能把侦察机砸掉。之后利用旁边的炮台攻击火神兽，以后看到炮台攻击就可以了，后文不再提及。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image019_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"再向前走，有三个侦察机，还是让阿陨站住不用，爬上左侧的山，用磁铁抓住铁块集落侦察机。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image021_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"然后地上有铁板，我们举着铁板向前走，前方不用多余操作，直接用铁板就能摧毁侦察机。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image023_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"最后三个侦察机，要通过气流到上方。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image025_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"到了上方就有铁块使用了，用铁块集落侦察机后，可以用铁矿砸最后的两个大蜥蜴人。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image027_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"用最后一个炮台攻击火神兽之后，就可以进入火神兽内部了。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image029_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"火神兽内部"},{"type":"text","content":"进入内部后，里面一片漆黑，能看见的就是火光和眼睛，先用弓箭把眼睛都打掉，然后拿火把取火，一个接一个的点亮灯台。找到勇导石，就可以点亮整个屋内了。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image031_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"在第二个房间可以看到第一个终端，我们调整神兽倾斜，即可拿到。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image033_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第二个终端在第一个屋子里，被树叶遮住，用火烧掉树叶，然后用磁力抓取器推开门即可。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image035_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第三个终端，要用蓝火点亮火把，倾斜神兽，从斜坡上去。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image037_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"到了外部之后向左转，下面有个烛台，点着即可。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image039_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"接着用倾斜、放平，将小球运下去，第三个终端就会出现。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image041_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第四个终端也在第一个门，这里掏出木箭，然后用蓝火点着。旁边有个小眼，把蓝火箭射进去，门就开了。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image043_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"另一边有树叶，点着之后，掉下来一个铁块，利用铁块和倾斜神兽通过火焰。解锁第三个终端。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image045_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"最后一个在外部的脊椎出，也要利用倾斜来解锁。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image047_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"全部终端解锁后，在外侧控制台准备BOSS战。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image049_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"火咒盖侬打法：第一阶段，利用弓箭射击他的眼睛，他的所有招式只要不停移动就能躲开。"},{"type":"text","content":"第二阶段，他会吸入物体，我们拿出炸弹，丢向他，然后引爆即可。"},{"type":"text","content":"第三阶段，他会砸地放出上升气流，我们可以顺着气流到上方攻击BOSS。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image051_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"战胜BOSS后，获得【英杰达尔克尔的守护】，按住ZL可以自动弹反，此招式主要提升弹反容错率，回到鼓隆城，与布尔多对话完成任务，在他家的宝箱内获得【碎岩巨剑】。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image053_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"全部神兽讨伐完毕后，与英帕对话，完成解放四神兽任务。接下来就要挑战最终BOSS了。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2019/08/20190828_syj_380_10/image055_S.jpg"}]}]},{"name":"迷你挑战","key":"mini","content":[{"name":"拉姆达大盗得财报（双子驿站）","content":[{"type":"title","content":"这个任务需要我们找到双子驿站附近埋藏的宝物 完成可以获得一把火焰大剑"},{"type":"text","content":"任务在双子驿站触发"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/988e1c532f632385aed48924cce833e038725d7b.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/38332303bbea3e8666aa0af65cd4483105eb557b.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"进入驿站和里面对话的两个海拉尔人对话 触发任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/05aae8a75f0f822b2a0c7787c018512c8df14d7b.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/8db0c6a726334884ab012099ddee7b7f870e457b.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"宝藏地点在驿站正下方的瀑布位置"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/874f6275e5f4fcf580ef517b21d7726b0de2bd7b.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"顺着河流走 就可以看到瀑布 瀑布下面的石头上还有个呀哈哈"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/732a12e265e7340f119a7f9635b9763e20c2b47b.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/bff8683e21c2bbd69a32065d116186254093ae7b.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"爬上瀑布 使用炸弹炸开石壁 在里面可以发现很多装着宝石的宝箱"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/87645f93cee8b004d6f9baba79260d9a300ea97b.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/f367139a310e179961c8d10dc9406afec214a37b.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"再炸开里面的石壁 打开宝箱 获得火焰大剑 最后回去和那两个海拉尔人对话就可以完成任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/c255efc595ee41c127c5c7e68d88912ca4ca9b7b.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ad121888912ca5ca490afbfd8bfc77f7990e947b.jpg"}]},{"name":"捕捉野生马匹 (双子驿站)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"捕捉野生马匹是一个教程任务，通过这个任务可以教会我们如何捕捉马匹"},{"type":"text","content":"任务接取在双子驿站 和驿站门口的npc对话就可以触发"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/35f2224133bad341cfcc7d82427622bc7cc52c0b.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3d002dbad341037d2c8655c3a9bc7dc5ce672d0b.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"这个挑战需要我们在限时两分钟内抓住一匹马 并带回去登陆"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/32fbcd41037de13707c7be09f6c5cf672a5f2a0b.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"在驿站外的草地就有很多马匹 先加速跑过去 然后在草中潜行 慢慢挪到马屁股位置"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/d2001d7de137c976ed0de17044672b5fd4462b0b.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"靠近后 立即上马 安抚马匹 就可以成功驯服（马身上斑纹越多 马就越容易抓）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/023cff37c97622bcad7453d2a05fd5460496280b.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"最后带着马匹 到驿站注册"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/e076d77622bc7dc51ed6b7ea5e460596b914290b.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/c8373cbc7dc5cf67f9ee49f38e96b814f5d0260b.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"最后和npc对话就可以完成任务 奖励有50块"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/04d7a614f4d0b5031060da4bcc4ec28332bf2008.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b955ead0b503c8d29f4cdbfb498333bf3aef2108.jpg"}]},{"name":"巨大马匹捕捉大作战","content":[{"type":"title","content":"巨大马匹捕捉大作战"},{"type":"text","content":"巨大马匹捕捉大作战是游戏的支线任务， 需要我们抓捕游戏中的唯一一匹巨型马王 "},{"type":"text","content":"任务接取在高原驿站左侧的骑射演武场"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/bf6e59704618dfda7728373589214f57925677aa.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"和演武场报名npc边上的npc对话就可以触发任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3ac71c214f579356cba8f493effb960b302170aa.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/04201aa355e983ae49c4559968efe078153169aa.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"任务需要我们找到巨马给任务npc看 我们可以传送到下图的神庙 再往神庙后面的面包树位置飞行"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/e2aefe781431dfb6957f5bd512cf02532e6363aa.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/332d496699cf025384702f366b36e29146e85faa.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"在山头 用希卡之石可以看到树下有很多马匹 其中带头的黑色巨马就是任务目标 （后面的黑马可以刷出高属性马匹）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/e3d059e833e039728f10b759b5863048604356aa.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"直接滑翔的马背位置可以直接上马"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/38332303bbea3e86855b6df05cd4483105eb55aa.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/6002c9d4483104eb4cb453bc092b74ee1d324eaa.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"驯服后骑马到任务npc那就可以完成任务奖励是银卢比（不要忘了在驿站登记哦）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/1d735518512c8cf11ab42a80c384cde34a2c46aa.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"重要的沙球(西哈特尔)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"需要帮助精灵库柏林 找回它的沙球 完成后就可以找它增加装备栏了"},{"type":"text","content":"任务接取在沿着卡卡利科桥往北走的小路边"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/03f26bd7997bbbf4c295546e5549610f8a56d660.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"在路边有个胖嘟嘟的树精灵 和他对话接取任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/739bc049610f8b56b0c908dc9ce951e10ff8d360.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"任务要帮他找回沙球 按着地图提示 穿过石洞 可以发现好几个哥布林"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ac45306817e951e12f357ee25e3da824d9e9cf60.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/5917cb3da824d8e9ea1f9dd2da598540112ac860.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"击杀哥布林 解锁怪物宝箱 打开就是我们要的沙球了"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ba274f598540102a2f2f1816b142a07aa110c560.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3b03be7aa010bc33ddf5120f92efa25f0d143f61.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"回到精灵那 对话 就可以升级装备栏 完成任务了 "},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a31e1214c27bd282be4487f23cb1eef97ebd3661.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/efb861bd4c7c34b3038c150e5841037de0373161.jpg"}]},{"name":"珂珂娜的厨房(卡卡利科村)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"珂珂娜的厨房 是卡卡利特村的支线任务 任务有4个阶段 需要找到不同的食材让珂珂娜制作午饭"},{"type":"text","content":"任务接取在卡卡利特村"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b666b2530688912ce119675c1b4800fc76f7976b.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"白天到位置和篝火边的小孩对话接取任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/5e9a2820b93acd8970169dbb0335dd8a58de8b6b.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第一阶段 需要速速胡萝卜 在村子的菜地就可以获得 交给npc就可以获得速速蔬菜浓汤"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3931cb413a8ca608fedc2f48db8c9bcec6f8fe6b.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/2e66f9ef28066b01fa0e88f43df39187021cf36b.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第二阶段  需要奶油 在利特村的商店可以购买 交给npc可以获得奶油苹果"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/bfa52adaf05e4a230ea245a91dd818196020e26b.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/7496877bbbf4da58f60965fdea0f8b56ac04d76b.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第三阶段 需要兽肉 在野外狩猎野兽就可以获得 交给npc可以获得坚硬南瓜镶肉"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/d9a8d2d2bb6651591193ab9e8fe23ea23b42c76b.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/35fa07efa25f0c1463a869360d89a146b6b13868.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第四阶段 需要蜂蜜 森林树上的蜂巢就是 交给npc可以获得精力蜂蜜苹果"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3d002dbad341037d4fe472c2a9bc7dc5ce672d68.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b955ead0b503c8d2fc2dfcfa498333bf3aef2168.jpg"}]},{"name":"和普莉珂玩吧!(卡卡利科村)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"和普莉珂玩吧！是在卡卡利科村的支线任务 需要我们陪普莉珂一块玩耍"},{"type":"text","content":"任务卡卡利特村接取"},{"type":"image","content":"https://s1.imagehub.cc/images/2024/08/27/1930c6ed92fbfbcd13cf47a7c30c6a3d.png"},{"type":"text","content":"白天在村子的街道上有个奔跑的小孩和对话触发任务。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://s1.imagehub.cc/images/2024/08/27/f198ae81c59cf9eb8ba3bf582b5fec2c.png"},{"type":"text","content":"任务需要陪他玩耍"},{"type":"image","content":"https://s1.imagehub.cc/images/2024/08/27/129abe7c89aed9d71e2856a6b7c6ce61.png"},{"type":"text","content":"警察抓小偷，直接冲刺碰到他就可以完成 \n 躲猫猫，我们需要找到他躲藏的位置，就在英帕房子的后面，上楼梯右转的屋子面就可以发现"},{"type":"image","content":"https://s1.imagehub.cc/images/2024/08/27/f3de08d999ec990161f8eef5f857267b.png"},{"type":"image","content":"https://s1.imagehub.cc/images/2024/08/27/6f0ede80475a870b28ac9b84e9c629b9.png"},{"type":"text","content":"对话后，就可以完成任务获得奖励"},{"type":"image","content":"https://s1.imagehub.cc/images/2024/08/27/6c7a4cb5b45360719cc831dce189ab7f.png"}]},{"name":"萤火虫之光(卡卡利科村)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"萤火虫之光是一个挑战任务，需要需要抓萤火虫来实现一个少女的愿望，下面给大家介绍。"},{"type":"text","content":"任务在卡卡利科村触发"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/c8373cbc7dc5cf67e1bb71f38e96b814f5d0267e.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"在夜间 到村子里面 穿过木桥的房子里 有个女性npc（白天会在服装店门外揽客）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/23fd63c5cf672b5f1ea2a1233314f4d0b403277e.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/7c84d1672b5fd546c9721ca17fd0b503c9d2247e.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"和她对话 了解她想要在屋子里看到萤火虫"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ce26355fd546059675f050653e03c8d247fe257e.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/2a1ecb460596b8143a3411b643d246fe464e227e.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"出门 在木桥边就有很多静静萤火虫 （穿着忍者套 萤火虫就不会乱跑 让你抓）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/d4071b96b814f4d07ae76c67cdfe474ec383237e.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"抓住5只后回到房间 打开背包拿出萤火虫在npc面前 放出来 就可以完成任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/04d7a614f4d0b5031836e24bcc4ec28332bf207e.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b955ead0b503c8d2971ae3fb498333bf3aef217e.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"任务奖励是紫色卢比有80块"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/f591ab03c8d246fe95aa6636b8bf3bef344f1e7e.jpg"}]},{"name":"照相机和希卡感应器(哈特诺古代研究所)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"迷你挑战 照相机和希卡感应器任务其实就是教你使用照相机 解锁图鉴"},{"type":"text","content":"任务在哈诺特古代研究所"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/2184380f8835dd8a81a272b403013870d44187d3.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"进去和这个男NPC对话就可以接到任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a44e8afc508c9bce2484bdc4d6dd884ce44afad3.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"任务需要拍一张 暖暖蘑菇照片 在屋子后面就能找到"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/e6ae36066b0192ddde3c81401a87031c98c0f0d3.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b7b28f87031c99c05d80d635af2fa872951fedd3.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"回去对话 后还需要3个暖暖蘑菇才能完成任务 到指定的森林用感应器查找非常简单就能获得"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/256eb672941fbee4cca6c7edc1237971ff1de7d3.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/7830e01d96d818199e5c907e876efbf203b3ded3.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a68c126efbf202b371aaaec830f4da5873dadbd3.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"之后回去就可以完成任务  以后还可以在这花钱就可以解锁所有图鉴"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/739bc049610f8b56a17919db9ce951e10ff8d3d3.jpg"}]},{"name":"欣欣向荣吧!樱达建筑店(哈特诺村)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"欣欣向荣吧樱达建筑店这个任务需要我们帮助npc松达建设新的村落，下面给大家介绍任务的详细攻略。"},{"type":"text","content":"任务需要在哈洛特村购买房屋后 再到死亡之山下方的一始村触发"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ccc83ec5260f88352f2b456dce07880139708634.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"和村里的松达对话就可以触发任务 任务有很多阶段 第一次需要给npc10个木头"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3931cb413a8ca6085fae884fdb8c9bcec6f8fe34.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/c6b994775ddd884ce7e833946cef28066a01f634.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第二次对话需要招募一个鼓隆族的npc （这个任务招募的村民名字都叫xx达）\n\n这个npc在鼓隆城下面的南部采矿场"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/6a408cdd3340b6f39b251faf12c0affce086ee34.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"和在挖矿的npc格莱达对话就可以招募"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/256eb672941fbee42778ecedc1237971ff1de734.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ff5c88d818196120bc6f10dd70f202b374d7df34.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第三次对话 需要20个木头"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/7496877bbbf4da585178c2faea0f8b56ac04d734.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第四次对话 需要招募一个会裁缝的npc 位置就在格鲁德小镇边上的卡拉卡集市"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/50a010f85856d53d8686c45a47d2bb665059ca34.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/50189b40102a04e2080026f12b7aa010bd33c234.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"和帐篷下的npc帕吾达 对话就可以招募（白天）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a13bbe10bc33ec380819055c295f0c14c37b3c35.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/35fa07efa25f0c1482d9ce310d89a146b6b13835.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第五次对话需要30个木头"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a31e1214c27bd282c42bbdf53cb1eef97ebd3635.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第六次对话需要招募个开杂货铺的npc npc就在利特村 和村里一直坐在看台的npc培达 对话即可招募（白天）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a007a9b1eef97fbd0bde2800b74133bad2413335.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3d002dbad341037dac95d5c5a9bc7dc5ce672d35.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/c8373cbc7dc5cf6779fdc9f58e96b814f5d02635.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第七次 需要给他50个木头"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b955ead0b503c8d21f5c5bfd498333bf3aef2135.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"给完后 再次找他对话就会触发他订婚的消息 让后需要给他找个牧师 举办婚礼 这个npc就是卓拉领地 的npc卡颇达（小老婆的老师）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/460fdc8333bf3bef6bed4c0b3f3ea8db564a1a35.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/cf6d451b1edef4dccc9b0fac45ecd3d968750c35.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"找到牧师后  回去找松达对话 还需要找到他以前的工友参加婚礼 也就是林克家门口的粉色npc"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/125ed0ecd3d969758366f02ad243040149fe0935.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"全部准备好后 回到一始村参加婚礼（肌肉新娘）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/58021a0148fe1e422ac91862c2299a8838130335.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"参加完婚礼就可以完成任务奖励有2个钻石（此外村里旅馆不花钱 还解锁了一个隐藏商店）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/059057299a8839139447f05d26bcbe2f46707c35.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/bf6e59704618dfda6799273589214f5792567735.jpg"}]},{"name":"幸福搬运匠 (哈特诺村)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"幸福搬运匠任务具体操作如下："},{"type":"text","content":"玩家要先去到游戏幸福搬运匠任务区域，如图所示"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/c6b994775ddd884c079513906cef28066a01f67a.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"玩家还需要带30捆木材给NPC，然后就可以开始幸福搬运匠任务了。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/6a408cdd3340b6f37b583fab12c0affce086ee7a.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"然后玩家去到森林区域，使用斧头砍树，就可以获得木柴捆，玩家要获得带30捆木材。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/939c2d40b6f39187e8c3a57724fce186252fef7a.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"最后玩家返回任务区域，和NPC对话选择交付30捆木材，这样就可以通关幸福搬运匠任务了。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3201a8f39187031c751f934b6a86242fa972ec7a.jpg"}]},{"name":"送给爱人的礼物(哈特诺村)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"送给爱人的礼物是游戏的支线任务，这个任务需要帮助npc准备送给旅馆老板的礼物"},{"type":"text","content":"任务在哈特诺村接取"},{"type":"text","content":"在村子里面的马棚边有个男性海拉尔人 和他对话 触发任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/562787cf02532f632f734c83699147e832e05c4f.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/988e1c532f632385edc04e24cce833e038725d4f.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"任务需要帮他问出旅店老板喜欢的东西 到旅馆 和npc对话了解她喜欢精力蚂蚱想要100个在她边上乱跳（应该是敷衍的回答）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/031231632385e036ec67eb5db8e039723c035a4f.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"之后回去向npc说明 他会让你先找10个蚂蚱给他当作起步 "},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/8b3643dd884ce54a5cd14b5aa3066b0193ddf74f.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"蚂蚱在村子周围的草丛有非常多搜集10个后交给npc就可以完成任务 奖励有100块"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/5c9c964ce54a2f27931984b3e00192dd3240f44f.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/890dfb4a2f27e7ef5df0c7b419dd3340b7f3f54f.jpg"}]},{"name":"可恶的偷羊贼(哈特诺村)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"可恶的偷羊贼是哈诺特村的支线任务，需要帮助村姑赶走村外的偷羊贼"},{"type":"text","content":"任务在哈诺特村触发"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/84010e2a04e23ea2c00df9c92b10bc33ed38c3e6.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"和村子后山上的少女对话触发任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a31e1214c27bd28283d9f8f53cb1eef97ebd36e7.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3d002dbad341037df16790c5a9bc7dc5ce672de7.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"任务需要帮助少女解决村外偷羊的怪物  位置就在右侧的海岸"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ce26355fd5460596a044ad633e03c8d247fe25e7.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/f591ab03c8d246fe5a1e9b30b8bf3bef344f1ee7.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"到位置可以发现一个怪物巢穴 击杀所有怪物 解锁怪物宝箱就算完成"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/460fdc8333bf3bef141f090b3f3ea8db564a1ae7.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/560be432939c2cf7f6e285aa452c5b1b1fde12e7.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/def3c219ce2c5b1b338ead6f2b39131fcfec0ee7.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"最后回到少女那可以获得任务奖励银卢比（还有少女的芳心）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/cfadcdd96975f2c4d9c900f08f0148fe1f4206e7.jpg"}]}]},{"name":"神庙挑战","key":"shenmiao","content":[{"name":"神庙挑战列表","content":[{"type":"title","content":"神庙挑战列表"},{"type":"text","content":"1. \n 任务名称:【骷髅的左眼】\n 地点:【阿卡莱古代研究所】\n NPC:【洁琳】"},{"type":"text","content":"2. \n 任务名称:【前往漩涡状中心】\n 地点:【马秋兹半岛】\n NPC:【古老的石板】"},{"type":"text","content":"3. \n 任务名称:【孤岛的试炼】\n 地点:【洛美岛】\n NPC:【奇异的声音】"},{"type":"text","content":"4. \n 任务名称:【力量之泉的传说】\n 地点:【东阿卡莱驿站】\n NPC:【诺波坦】"},{"type":"text","content":"5. \n 任务名称:【鼓隆的毅力崖挑战】\n 地点:【毅力崖】\n NPC:【巴恺忒】"},{"type":"text","content":"6. \n 任务名称:【弟​弟在何方】\n 地点:【鼓隆城】\n NPC:【布莱顿】"},{"type":"text","content":"7. \n 任务名称:【驿站的风景画】\n 地点:【山麓驿站】\n NPC:【桑伏】"},{"type":"text","content":"8. \n 任务名称:【寻求玉液琼浆】\n 地点:【东格鲁德】\n NPC:【帕可忒】"},{"type":"text","content":"9. \n 任务名称:【比耐力】\n 地点:【娜波‌露山】\n NPC:【巴恺忒】"},{"type":"text","content":"10. \n 任务名称:【去影子指示的地方】\n 地点:【格鲁德之塔】\n NPC:【卡西瓦】"},{"type":"text","content":"11. \n 任务名称:【不会说话的剑士】\n 地点:【格鲁德小镇】\n NPC:【拉亦娜】"},{"type":"text","content":"12. \n 任务名称:【沙漠的试炼】\n 地点:【南洛美城堡遗迹】\n NPC:【奇异的声音】"},{"type":"text","content":"13. \n 任务名称:【七位英雄】\n 地点:【格鲁德小镇】\n NPC:【罗汀】"},{"type":"text","content":"14. \n 任务名称:【消失的沙尘暴？】\n 地点:【卡拉卡拉集市】\n NPC:【诺比尔】"},{"type":"text","content":"15. \n 任务名称:【雪山的日志】\n 地点:【摩尔迦娜山】\n NPC:【雪山的日志】"},{"type":"text","content":"16. \n 任务名称:【不败的女王】\n 地点:【沙海象拉力赛报名处】\n NPC:【帕弗宇】"},{"type":"text","content":"17. \n 任务名称:【不要践踏花儿】\n 地点:【海利亚河】\n NPC:【奥可芭】"},{"type":"text","content":"18. \n 任务名称:【巨人三兄弟的秘密】\n 地点:【泰尔美山】\n NPC:【古老的石碑】"},{"type":"text","content":"19. \n 任务名称:【三棵杉树的秘密】\n 地点:【哈特诺村】\n NPC:【可莱维亚】"},{"type":"text","content":"20. \n 任务名称:【被诅咒的石像】\n 地点:【哈特诺堡垒】\n NPC:【卡里尤】"},{"type":"text","content":"21. \n 任务名称:【寻找石碑碎块】\n 地点:【雅西诺遗迹】\n NPC:【利迦尼】"},{"type":"text","content":"22. \n 任务名称:【被盗的宝珠】\n 地点:【卡卡利科村】\n NPC:【帕雅】"},{"type":"text","content":"23. \n 任务名称:【想见见守护者！】\n 地点:【帕发海岸】\n NPC:【柳奈】"},{"type":"text","content":"24. \n 任务名称:【闪电开启的试炼】\n 地点:【克拉尔湖】\n NPC:【卡西瓦】"},{"type":"text","content":"25. \n 任务名称:【吞食巨蛇的龙】\n 地点:【思古兰特树海】\n NPC:【卡西瓦】"},{"type":"text","content":"26. \n 任务名称:【野外的试炼】\n 地点:【赛哈特诺岛】\n NPC:【奇异的声音】"},{"type":"text","content":"27. \n 任务名称:【高耸入云的山上有棵参天大树】\n 地点:【利特村】\n NPC:【桃虹】"},{"type":"text","content":"28. \n 任务名称:【利特的兄弟岩】\n 地点:【利特村】\n NPC:【奇尔】"},{"type":"text","content":"29. \n 任务名称:【利特的诗迷】\n 地点:【利特村】\n NPC:【蓓拉】"},{"type":"text","content":"30. \n 任务名称:【断崖的试炼】\n 地点:【北洛美城堡遗迹】\n NPC:【奇异的声音】"},{"type":"text","content":"31. \n 任务名称:【探索拉聂尔山的宝贝！】\n 地点:【哈特诺村】\n NPC:【西默茨凯】"},{"type":"text","content":"32. \n 任务名称:【英杰祭祀诗】\n 地点:【卓拉领地】\n NPC:【鲁拉曲】"},{"type":"text","content":"33. \n 任务名称:【两杆枪野兽】\n 地点:【阿拉布平原】\n NPC:【卡西瓦】"},{"type":"text","content":"34. \n 任务名称:【御风拓路者】\n 地点:【荷隆湾】\n NPC:【卡西瓦】"},{"type":"text","content":"35. \n 任务名称:【最初的试炼】\n 地点:【克洛格森林】\n NPC:【泰奇奥】"},{"type":"text","content":"36. \n 任务名称:【两个环】\n 地点:【西海拉鲁平原】\n NPC:【卡西瓦】"},{"type":"text","content":"37. \n 任务名称:【暗黑的试炼】\n 地点:【德依布朗遗迹】\n NPC:【奇异的声音】"},{"type":"text","content":"38. \n 任务名称:【红月之夜】\n 地点:【海拉鲁丘陵】\n NPC:【卡西瓦】"},{"type":"text","content":"39. \n 任务名称:【绝壁花纹】\n 地点:【塔邦挞大桥驿站】\n NPC:【果戈】"},{"type":"text","content":"40. \n 任务名称:【操控力的试炼】\n 地点:【克洛格森林】\n NPC:【阿兹基】"},{"type":"text","content":"41. \n 任务名称:【不燃烧的试炼】\n 地点:【克洛格森林】\n NPC:【达秘达米】"},{"type":"text","content":"42. \n 任务名称:【雷鸣的试炼】\n 地点:【雷之台地】\n NPC:【奇异的声音】"}]},{"name":"骷髅的左眼","content":[{"type":"title","content":"骷髅的左眼"},{"type":"text","content":"这个任务很简单 \n 在地图右上角古代研究所，里面女研究员就是任务接取npc"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/023cff37c97622bc5cd884d2a05fd546049628b6.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"对话了解任务提示  接到骷髅的左眼 任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/c99358fe474ec2831ea2705abe4f50b8b53e1cb6.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"骷髅的左眼就是地图右上角的骷髅头形状的湖（注意在右眼上）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/92dd32f7dfb2dc19f73110ae95def4dca13910b6.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"这是个寻找神庙的任务 所以找到后直接进去打开宝箱就可以通关 可获得一个火焰剑 "},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/f385f299594304010ee355f7d66b04d1482905b6.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"此外 异度之刃二联动的套装，有一个是在这个神庙上晚上看天会有流星从天而降"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/edafb3bcbe2f47701405946f6f3b3b86032179b6.jpg"}]},{"name":"前往旋涡状中心","content":[{"type":"title","content":"前往旋涡状中心"},{"type":"text","content":"前往漩涡状中心是一个神庙试炼，完成可以解锁利塔兹摩神庙"},{"type":"text","content":"任务位置在地图左侧海域的漩涡海滩上"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/51f9aa3ea8db574a3b102d29a7f7dfb2dd1917b8.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"环形海滩边上有个遗迹 进去就可以触发任务"},{"type":"text","content":"完成方法很简单，首先要捡起遗迹里的球"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b57fb6db574afa3251be924254b2dc19cf2c14b8.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"然后搬运到漩涡的中心 路上需要躲避怪物 （可以使用时间静止配合回旋斩 把球打到中心）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a99a494afa32939cefd561075719ce2c5a1b15b8.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/560be432939c2cf71b9062ac452c5b1b1fde12b8.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"中心位置有个机关 把球放到机关里就可以了"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/fb738d9c2cf7dfb2193b7099d01b1edef5dc13b8.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"放好后 中心位置就会升起言哨特利塔兹摩神庙"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/49c5d3e34b2c56ee6d5c38bbf775e5f4fdf540b8.jpg"}]},{"name":"力量之泉的传说","content":[{"type":"title","content":"力量之泉的传说"},{"type":"text","content":"任务触发在东阿卡莱驿站 \n 白天和驿站外篝火边的npc对话触发（第二个选项）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ba274f598540102aec0b5711b142a07aa110c57c.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/d3c39889a146b7b11610160ec77c34b33d41357d.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"任务需要火龙的鳞片 在死亡火山北部的奥汀大化石位置可以看到（06:00）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/e076d77622bc7dc5cb8d42ec5e460596b914297d.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/f591ab03c8d246fe4aa4ab30b8bf3bef344f1e7d.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"获得鳞片后到要到力量之泉 "},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b57fb6db574afa328476454454b2dc19cf2c147d.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"到力量之泉 把鳞片放到水里 就可以解锁神庙 完成任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/5a5a00def4dca03933f5a75f58d96975f3c40d7d.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/f385f29959430401601477f1d66b04d14829057d.jpg"}]},{"name":"鼓隆的毅力崖挑战","content":[{"type":"title","content":"鼓隆的毅力崖挑战"},{"type":"text","content":"鼓隆的毅力崖挑战是一个神庙试炼任务，完成就可以进入古阿齐托神庙"},{"type":"text","content":"任务位置在 火山边上的毅力崖"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/0fb94656d53da8244e4f7967306651598440cb3f.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"顺着气流飞到山崖顶 就可以发现神庙 和神庙门前的鼓隆族人 对话就会触发任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/5917cb3da824d8e95b740ed3da598540112ac83f.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/d47cb624d8e9ccd223c0e4ec0e40102a05e2c93f.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"任务需要在限定时间内从山脚爬到山顶（建议用攀登套 和至少两环精力）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a965c6e9ccd2bb66c8ff30f59b2a04e23fa2c63f.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"途中有可以休息的平台 和很多卢比 "},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/d695563104ebf6a74da8379effee1c324a184f3c.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"爬上去后就可以解锁神庙了（以后缺钱可以在这刷钱）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/49701aebf6a75f0f918cc15b97324b18502c4c3c.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/05aae8a75f0f822b6049a987c018512c8df14d3c.jpg"}]},{"name":"驿站的风景画","content":[{"type":"title","content":"驿站的风景画"},{"type":"text","content":"驿站的风景画是一个神庙试炼任务，完成可以解锁塔姆尔神庙"},{"type":"text","content":"任务触发在山麓驿站"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b6f0f0f97fbd4c7c6b7239f2b8bad341027d3014.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"在驿站里有个看壁画的npc，对话就可以触发任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/e076d77622bc7dc5a7a62eec5e460596b9142914.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ce26355fd5460596d4d5f1633e03c8d247fe2514.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"任务需要我们按着画找到神庙，神庙位置就在驿站左侧的山谷里。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b442d6d246fe474eb042360cb0ef354f51b81f14.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"到位置可以发现塔姆尔神庙"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/c3c22dbf3bef354f2679b18d23db574afb321b14.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b57fb6db574afa32e85d294454b2dc19cf2c1414.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"之后再回到驿站，和任务npc对话就可以完成这个神庙试炼任务了"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/fb738d9c2cf7dfb2a2d8cb9fd01b1edef5dc1314.jpg"}]},{"name":"寻求玉液琼浆","content":[{"type":"title","content":"寻求玉液琼浆"},{"type":"text","content":"寻求玉液琼浆是一个神庙试炼任务，需要我们帮助快渴死的npc找到冷饮"},{"type":"text","content":"任务位置在沙漠右侧的神庙"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/90c61d1c99c0affcc439219c2372941fbfe4ea11.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"找到神庙 发现放希卡之石的位置被一个npc挡住了 对话后就可以触发任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/256eb672941fbee41e65f5edc1237971ff1de711.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"任务需要我们帮他找冷饮  到格鲁德小镇的冷饮店 和老板对话"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/359bee5e4a237971d0a2936b93196120a6cde311.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"对话了解需要帮助老板运冰块 冰块就在村子正北方向的冰屋\n到冰屋 和里面的npc对话 就会给你冰块"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/979906196120a7cd3fd1fe4189b375d7987bdc11.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"之后需要我们快速搬起冰块在他融化前穿越冰屋与小镇间的废墟 "},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/0d2fe5f202b375d7aec4be47515872dadf49d811.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/bab5c45872dade495db08ee526042e6816e9d511.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"成功后 就可以回到神庙前告诉任务npc冷饮做好了 他就会飞奔的离开 这样我们就可以进入神庙完成任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/8a17b3042e6817e9105e0b4bd356d53da924ce11.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/0fb94656d53da8249e56c961306651598440cb11.jpg"}]},{"name":"去影子指示的地方","content":[{"type":"title","content":"去影子指示的地方"},{"type":"text","content":"去影子指示的地方是一个神庙试炼任务，完成可以解锁萨萨卡伊神庙任"},{"type":"text","content":"前往格鲁德之塔塔顶，上面有个拉手风琴的利特族，对话可以接到任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/2947750192dd33408fad7d33881c99c0aefcf1f6.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"来到格鲁德之塔南方的位置，找到一个祭坛"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ff5c88d818196120ec93e0da70f202b374d7dff6.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"祭坛未开启时是橙色亮光，成功开启后是蓝光"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/16a84fe10ef858568863449053e9ccd2ba66cdf6.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"用木柴点一个篝火，将时间消磨到中午"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ed792abb19efa25f634a2ecf59828689a0463bf7.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"等到15:20左右的时候，塔的影子会移到祭坛上"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/023cff37c97622bcfd9b23d3a05fd546049628f7.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"此时用弓箭对准太阳，射箭"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3aae2b4f50b8b43e3985bbfe7132939c2df719f7.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"祭坛旁边神庙出现。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/f385f29959430401eda0f2f6d66b04d1482905f7.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"总结\n\n \n\n1.  格鲁德之塔塔顶接任务；\n\n2.  找到格鲁德之塔南方的祭坛；\n\n3.  祭坛是否开启可以通过颜色分辨；\n\n4.  点篝火消磨时间到中午；\n\n5.  15:20塔影移到祭坛上；\n\n6.  对准太阳射箭；\n\n7.  祭坛出现。"}]},{"name":"不会说话的剑士","content":[{"type":"title","content":"不会说话的剑士"},{"type":"text","content":"不会说话的剑士 是格鲁德小镇的一个神庙挑战任务 需要根据沙地中的雕像所指的方向找到基玛兹斯神庙完成任务"},{"type":"text","content":"任务触发在格鲁德小镇兵营边上的门"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/988e1c532f632385c0057b22cce833e038725d8a.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"和后门把守的守卫对话就可以触发任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/38332303bbea3e86187bf8f05cd4483105eb558a.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/1d735518512c8cf1ed94bf80c384cde34a2c468a.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"任务需要按照门前的雕像手指的位置走找到神庙  其实神庙就在卡尔萨谷边上 可以直接飞过去解锁"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/49c5d3e34b2c56ee404c1fbdf775e5f4fdf5408a.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/fdb4f00d3aceaad731589551eee7340f6578b88a.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"在神庙没解锁前 这个区域一直在刮沙尘暴 而这些雕像就是指引我们找到神庙的坐标  "},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/65390a23beb9763e6af122656ad06de89b61b08a.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"按着提示走最终可以发现一个遗迹 里面就可以找到基玛兹斯神庙 完成神庙试炼就可以让沙尘暴停止"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/6ca98461862541939cdb29b7df1bd10ff326ab8a.jpg"}]},{"name":"沙漠的试炼","content":[{"type":"title","content":"沙漠的试炼"},{"type":"text","content":"沙漠的试炼是个神庙试炼任务，完成可以解锁迪拉玛神庙获得蛮族服"},{"type":"text","content":"任务在沙漠右侧的迷宫"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/1562a0b9763e21c286444965e6e89a618725b12b.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第一次进入这个迷宫就可以触发任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/bff8683e21c2bbd6df42c55d116186254093ae2b.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"这个迷宫有个快速解密方法 就是飞到迷宫右下角的第二个洞"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/979906196120a7cd9cfc534789b375d7987bdc2b.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/19587f20a7cd0c6e6a60aa06fed7997bbaf4dd2b.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"飞下去可以看到有被盖侬污染的墙壁 在这个位置下去可以快速找到入口"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/6061b9cd0c6efbf29021dd62127bbbf4db58da2b.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a68c126efbf202b3e64531ce30f4da5873dadb2b.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"下去后往里走 可以发现边上有两个火炬的洞口 下去就可以发现迪拉玛神庙"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/0d2fe5f202b375d70de91341515872dadf49d82b.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/fab31cb375d7997b2e6672edf9dade49600fd92b.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"在迪拉玛神庙里的宝箱 可以开出蛮族服"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/03f26bd7997bbbf44ccada6f5549610f8a56d62b.jpg"}]},{"name":"消失的沙尘暴","content":[{"type":"title","content":"消失的沙尘暴"},{"type":"text","content":"消失的沙尘暴是 卡拉卡拉集市里的一个神庙挑战任务 需要找到达科塔瓦神庙 让沙漠的沙尘暴停止后完成"},{"type":"text","content":"任务触发在 卡拉卡拉集市"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/35f2224133bad341c3d84984427622bc7cc52c39.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"在集市边的瞭望台可以发现一个npc 对话就可以触发任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3d002dbad341037d209261c5a9bc7dc5ce672d39.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"这个npc说对面的沙尘暴里有宝物但无法进入 其实这个宝物就是达科塔瓦神庙 位置就在北格鲁德巨石上"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/c8373cbc7dc5cf67edfa7df58e96b814f5d02639.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"在村边可以看到远方的巨石 我们直接瞄准位置往前走就可以了 （靠近会有沙尘暴就无法看到方向）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b955ead0b503c8d28b5beffd498333bf3aef2139.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"解锁神庙后再和npc对话就可以完成任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/460fdc8333bf3befe7eaf80b3f3ea8db564a1a39.jpg"}]},{"name":"雪山的日记","content":[{"type":"title","content":"雪山的日志"},{"type":"text","content":"雪山的日志是雪山顶的一个神庙试炼，解谜成功可以解锁斯玛萨玛神庙"},{"type":"text","content":"任务地点在沙漠右侧的雪山顶。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/025d87c0affce186a7be00c71f1fbee435daeb2a.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"在雪山顶可以发现一个棚子，里面有本日记阅读后触发任务。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/9881b1fce186242f2ce33caa35e434daf15ee82a.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/aebdff86242fa872118e1651bfdaf05e4b23e92a.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"在棚子边上的水坑有小雪球 。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/e0c73a2fa872941f38759c6f7b5e4a237871e62a.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"抬起雪球扔向棚子后面的雪坡，滚成大雪球。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/256eb672941fbee4b34b58ebc1237971ff1de72a.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"抬起雪球往水池的那端走。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a9338a1fbee434da78cfe296f271fe1d97d8e42a.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":" 崖边可以看到一个机关，在16点举着雪球让影子挡住机关的中心，就可以解锁斯玛萨玛神庙完成任务。\n\n "},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/955ea0e434daf05ec3b2d1c4751d96d81919e52a.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/bfa52adaf05e4a23f3e056a81dd818196020e22a.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/fb738d9c2cf7dfb207886699d01b1edef5dc132b.jpg"}]},{"name":"不败的女王","content":[{"type":"title","content":"不败的女王"},{"type":"text","content":"不败的女王是一个神庙挑战任务，需要完成沙漠里的挑战赛解锁拉丘乌罗神庙"},{"type":"text","content":"任务位置在格鲁德小镇右侧的废墟"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/739bc049610f8b560698b6db9ce951e10ff8d333.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"到地点是一个沙海象拉力赛报名处 和里面的npc对话 就可以触发任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/0fb94656d53da8246b755461306651598440cb33.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ba274f598540102abd7ea611b142a07aa110c533.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3b03be7aa010bc3353a4ac0892efa25f0d143f30.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"任务需要战胜比赛的冠军 需要在1分30秒的时间内完成任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a31e1214c27bd282401539f53cb1eef97ebd3630.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"比赛很简单 就是骑着沙海象 通过木头门形状的记录点 只要不失误时间肯定够用"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/4d3d2ab33c4133ba1cdd9bce6a37c97623bc2f30.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/23fd63c5cf672b5f02da9d253314f4d0b4032730.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"完成后就会获得奖杯 机关球 把球放进机关的凹槽就可以解锁拉丘乌罗神庙"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/dd58d02c5b1b1ede1b40388a981fceecd2d90f30.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/58021a0148fe1e42a6f79c62c2299a8838130330.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/92174dbbf82064fb9996a9928e6104a354e96f30.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"这个神庙可以直接打开宝箱 过关 奖励格鲁德的太阳盾"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/e1390a31dfb6326c4bfb017c89532f6322856030.jpg"}]},{"name":"巨人三兄弟的密码","content":[{"type":"title","content":"塔瓦·吉努神庙 巨人三兄弟的秘密攻略"},{"type":"text","content":"巨人三兄弟这个神庙需要偷巨人家族的珠宝"},{"type":"text","content":"神庙位置 在索尔美山顶"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/f0848bee41c1b727dbce833d1a2ca5cadde89836.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"四周有三个独眼巨人 在中间山顶有三个机关 和一个石碑 调查获得任务巨人三兄弟的秘密"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/91091efc77f7980edfbdc6c4d4db3620b83a9136.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"之后需要去边上的三个湿地 里面各有一个独眼巨人 脖子上挂着珠宝"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3761a73acd8920c5a1920d80568a59de44078836.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"巨人都在睡觉 可以爬到骨头上 飞到脖子上偷珠宝"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/dccb47de45078801b5ed50f4b18ca608a40f8236.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a749bb0f94fc508c0f53424d01775ddd894cfd36.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"把三个珠宝放到机关里就可以了，神庙里是把闪电剑"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/5c9c964ce54a2f277c72adb3e00192dd3240f436.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/939c2d40b6f39187a1811c7524fce186252fef36.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/256eb672941fbee49e4775ebc1237971ff1de736.jpg"}]},{"name":"三棵杉树的秘密","content":[{"type":"title","content":"三棵杉树的秘密"},{"type":"text","content":"三棵杉树的秘密 是一个神庙试炼任务"},{"type":"text","content":"在哈特诺村下图位置 我们可以触发任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/5e4e9c2b74ee1c32ade4b49807f1d8a727334b51.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"到位置可以看到一个望着湖面的小姐姐 和他对话触发"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/cca2552c56ee7b7f76f299c16ef4fcf5ef0d4151.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"这是个神庙任务 位置如下图 在村庄右上方的山脉"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/0da37be7340f6478e8df5b0dfd3e21c2bad6b551.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"到位置可以发现有几颗松树，里面还有个暗门 直接炸开就是神庙了"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/87645f93cee8b0045ce634bb79260d9a300ea951.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/6bbfdd14f1c595ee543c529327530688902c9a51.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"这个神庙是个外解密，所以进去直接开宝箱通关"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/994f412043715fdb15dd5c8e468920c5270f8c51.jpg"}]},{"name":"比耐力任务","content":[{"type":"title","content":"比耐力任务攻略"},{"type":"text","content":"这个神庙任务是个体感关卡"},{"type":"text","content":"神庙位置 不太好找 到地方可以看到三个石头人"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/5917cb3da824d8e909773cd3da598540112ac83e.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a965c6e9ccd2bb6696fc02f59b2a04e23fa2c63e.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"和石头人对话获得任务比耐力"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/cd93a56651598540d98f8357b5a23a42a17ac43e.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"这个比耐力 很简单 就是站在台子上会掉血  血少的话还可以吃药补血 大概消耗十几滴血后就可以过关"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/84010e2a04e23ea2f6e727cf2b10bc33ed38c33e.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a13bbe10bc33ec38e51e9e5a295f0c14c37b3c3f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"进入神庙会发现是个体感关卡 第一关其实直接一发闪电箭就可以过关 "},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/18aebc5f0c14c27b0427013c2a46b7b1eff9393f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"第二关需要用铁块压住右边的机关"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/d3c39889a146b7b1345cf808c77c34b33d41353f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"再把吹风机调节成X状，借风过去拿宝箱"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/32fbcd41037de1372ad3a509f6c5cf672a5f2a3f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/04d7a614f4d0b5032577c14bcc4ec28332bf203f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"之后踩住对面的机关 就可以解锁大门 时间静止过关"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3aae2b4f50b8b43e5e7ed0ff7132939c2df7193f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"七位英雄任务","content":[{"type":"title","content":"七位英雄任务攻略"},{"type":"text","content":"这个神庙是沙漠里那个神像的机关解密"},{"type":"text","content":"在女儿国村子下图位置的房间 找到npc对话获得七位英雄任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/9b2098254193cee8d2fadeae5a0ff2260c9aa857.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/87645f93cee8b00437e55bba79260d9a300ea957.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"然后到图中位置找到七个女神像，先到有灯的像上把球扔下去"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/40d2d0e8b004541bb5f17893869a310e1699a657.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/cfa9ae04541bd10f97d8872fba0e1799e82aa757.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b1454a1bd10ff2266b64bbbb9c99e92abbb8a457.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"球上都有个符号 要和神像上的符号对应（符号大部分在脚上 有两个在头上）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/2184380f8835dd8adc20cfb203013870d4418757.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"球都放进去 就可以解锁神庙"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/274e9635dd8a59dec3f902b4b370d5413b8c8457.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"神庙里是一把火焰枪"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/8974c38a59de45070fffb2c55e413a8ca7088557.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"不要践踏花儿","content":[{"type":"title","content":"不要践踏花儿"},{"type":"text","content":"【地区】哈特尔地区-西哈特尔"},{"type":"text","content":"【地点】海利亚河南边的花之中州"},{"type":"text","content":"【神庙】席罗·席拉神庙"},{"type":"text","content":"【条件】与花之中州的大树旁边的女子奥可芭对话，或者踩到了花之中州岛上的花儿之后触发对话，开启神庙挑战"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20210124/071e9a02cd77dd2143560b66fec2af6a.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20210124/a5c3c296c42e9aabd9683d79cdc5e62d.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"【达成】不要碰到任何花，在神庙周围沿着没有花的地方迂回绕道前进，直至到达【席罗·席拉神庙】入口并启动传送点。或者爬上女子旁边的大树顶部，从大树顶部使用滑翔帆飞到神庙入口处就OK，启动神庙传送点之后神庙挑战达成"},{"type":"text","content":"【提示】\n ★各种颜色的花都不能碰到，不能踩到，不能用武器攻击到 \n★碰到3次花朵之后，奥可芭会暴怒，很可怕，很可怕...林克会受到伤害喏 \n ★注意神庙入口处的道路中间有一簇花，小心别碰到"},{"type":"text","content":"方法一：迂回绕道"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20210124/341a6098debf0d177b7d81b200e6670d.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"方法二：滑翔帆"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20210124/89e8ef8edda835c493a7838593bab0d7.jpg"}]},{"name":"被诅咒的石像","content":[{"type":"title","content":"被诅咒的石像"},{"type":"text","content":"被诅咒的石像神庙位于法兰台地南边，到达位置后需要消耗时间到晚上，接着找到紫色目光石像，然后使用弓箭射击石像的眼睛即可解锁神庙。进入神庙后需要借助时停的能力停下齿轮，接着通过齿轮前往下一个石板，等齿轮再启动继续利用齿轮转到最上层即可过关。神庙具体过法如下："},{"type":"text","content":"一、神庙外部解谜"},{"type":"text","content":"1.来到法兰台地南边的峡谷位置。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20230407/6670948a6275e84b0eee23196fe7b87d.png"},{"type":"text","content":"2.达到位置后用木材生火，选择休息到晚上。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20230407/c1e6105b298dd1d0cc5830a6f66dc152.png"},{"type":"text","content":"3.入夜后在石像群中找到紫色眼睛的石像。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20230407/560ecf164a07f54bbbe4cd4bcc6e232a.png"},{"type":"text","content":"4.使用弓箭射击这个石像的眼睛。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20230407/db48af57bd005dd49f6f4244c5e4849b.png"},{"type":"text","content":"5.完成操作后神庙就会出现了。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20230407/644795cdc99b5a5491dc80ba3f68737f.png"},{"type":"text","content":"二、神庙内部过法"},{"type":"text","content":"1.进入神庙后通过中间的路前往圆盘内部。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20230407/88b95e2f1b80e303fe551191f281756a.png"},{"type":"text","content":"2.进入圆盘里面后停在转动的石板前面，跟随石板上升到上面去。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20230407/394c02e6b35927b033cfba8b12a52d2c.png"},{"type":"text","content":"3.在石板上升到与齿轮同一高度时，使用时停能力让齿轮停止转动。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20230407/71bd94410890c70e35112704846a29be.png"},{"type":"text","content":"4.在齿轮右边有一个宝箱。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20230407/83a1797a737001c49eb28327f7d5d9da.png"},{"type":"text","content":"5.打开宝箱获得蛋白石。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20230407/9bf069f2d57819330b38ac007f5d556d.png"},{"type":"text","content":"6.往圆盘里面看，在转动的石板上可以找到第二个宝箱。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20230407/216377250b9a67d45af8ea508147747e.png"},{"type":"text","content":"7.在确保石板转到可以站立的位置时，使用时停能力停下右边墙上的齿轮。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20230407/5642fa047c1fe8e43f4bb3b86a145949.png"},{"type":"text","content":"8.石板停止转动后跳到石板上。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20230407/ab45891e1f11f946742dbe1f9519c976.png"},{"type":"text","content":"9.打开宝箱得到骑士之枪。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20230407/0fe164778999b94a4f975fb152c1d69e.png"},{"type":"text","content":"10.接着再次来到齿轮这里，停下齿轮后通过齿轮前往对面平台。（重复2，3步骤到达齿轮）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20230407/e9d5f682b8c296f8fcfa03eaa28468f0.png"},{"type":"text","content":"11.到达对面的平台后站到齿轮的齿上。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20230407/9263d7214785aeb5f06aa5a9f80a0391.png"},{"type":"text","content":"12.跟随转动的齿轮来到对面的楼梯位置。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20230407/dcc12da962ca513d37515f2ca6e3374d.png"},{"type":"text","content":"13.等到楼梯转到合适位置后跑过去就好。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20230407/8b5fbb2dd499f2c3ca3fd840e744b0f6.png"},{"type":"text","content":"14.在通过楼梯后就可以来到导师位置了，与导师对话后就可以过关了。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20230407/f1a396ebdd551a83fd6e11838e737287.png"}]},{"name":"寻找石碑的碎片","content":[{"type":"title","content":"寻找石碑的碎片"},{"type":"text","content":"寻找石碑的碎块这个神庙挑战可以解锁玛·卡亚神庙 需要我们找到三个石碑的碎片（玩过黄昏公主的应该知道这个石碑就是黄昏之镜）"},{"type":"text","content":"任务位置在沃特里村右侧的海滩"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20210121/e5bdc3df42c0fc366507f20da66a6455.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20210121/7f87636f13a3aba8ec26f30d6546ab75.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"到位置可以发现三个神庙机关和一个npc\n\n对话就可以触发任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/vg/cover/20210121/ca8479334ffea75d3185d5f75196ffdc.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/static/frontend/img/lazyload/loading@gif_2.gif"},{"type":"text","content":"触发后用希卡之石可以看到三个碎片的照片\n\n第一个在月牙沙滩尖角位置的椰子树后面 （边上的石头有个呀哈哈）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/static/frontend/img/lazyload/loading@gif_2.gif"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/static/frontend/img/lazyload/loading@gif_2.gif"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/static/frontend/img/lazyload/loading@gif_2.gif"},{"type":"text","content":"第二个在遗迹右侧有个暗礁里，第三个再右侧的椰子树后面"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/static/frontend/img/lazyload/loading@gif_2.gif"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/static/frontend/img/lazyload/loading@gif_2.gif"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/static/frontend/img/lazyload/loading@gif_2.gif"},{"type":"text","content":"找到后，回到npc那，把照片给他看，再随便找个机关上面蹲着就可以解锁神庙完成任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/static/frontend/img/lazyload/loading@gif_2.gif"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/static/frontend/img/lazyload/loading@gif_2.gif"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.vgover.com/static/frontend/img/lazyload/loading@gif_2.gif"}]},{"name":"被盗走的宝珠","content":[{"type":"title","content":"被盗走的珠宝"},{"type":"text","content":"需要帮助卡卡利特村的帕雅找到被盗走的珠宝"},{"type":"text","content":"任务在 做完卡卡利特村的所有支线 触发其中就包括两个小女孩的迷你挑战（一个做饭 一个玩躲猫猫）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/bf6e59704618dfda0ca08c3389214f5792567731.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"之后再到帕英的住所 询问门前的守卫 了解珠宝被盗走了"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/46315818dfdae43bd21db594c457935652bb7431.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/4759c1dae43b3b86e8baf8e2185653bbf9207531.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"进屋 和帕雅对话 同意陪他一天来安抚她"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3b8fb4d7726b0ce2427b83baef781423bfb9b631.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ab966c6b0ce265e71c93d3cd9f23beb9773eb731.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"从帕雅房间出来 需要等到晚上 在街上有个女子畏畏缩缩 靠近她就会被发现 "},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/732a12e265e7340f4de4a39635b9763e20c2b431.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/0da37be7340f64783ebf090cfd3e21c2bad6b531.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"我们需要远远的跟着她 直到在村子后面的墓地 了解她只是偷偷祭拜死去的丈夫"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/64a62a0f647814239525c18baac2bbd6e0d0b231.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/354e7a781423beb95aa2967730d6e1d06ce8b331.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"弄错了后 再回到村子 发现之前的守卫 也在偷偷摸摸的走 远远跟着他进入后山的树林 就会发现他和依盖队的人对话"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/65390a23beb9763e0c5e0c636ad06de89b61b031.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/1562a0b9763e21c2954a5665e6e89a618725b131.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"上前 击杀依盖队的人 和守卫对话了解他曾今是依盖队的人 为了家人逃离依盖队在村子安居 但逃离时妻子被杀 一直隐瞒的两个孩子事实真相（其实孩子已经知道了）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/bff8683e21c2bbd6ce4cda5d116186254093ae31.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/777f3fc2bbd6e1d05d742dd40d254193cfe8af31.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"剧情过后把珠宝放到机关里就可以解锁拉纳·罗基神庙"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/d04eec260d9a310e2c055e9f31b842406bfea231.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/f367139a310e1799d5b60d0dc9406afec214a331.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/0cdb2f0e1799e92a8724f5f5e1fec314f0c5a031.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"进入神庙打开宝箱 就可以完成这个神庙试炼 完成这个任务了"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/304f0999e92abab87cdcdd4b4814f1c594eea131.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"吞食巨蛇的龙(希·库乔夫神庙)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"吞噬巨蛇的龙(希·库乔夫神庙)"},{"type":"text","content":"吞噬巨蛇的龙是一个神庙试炼，完成可以解锁勇气之泉的神庙"},{"type":"text","content":"任务触发位置如图"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/bf6e59704618dfda0e938e3389214f5792567702.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"在这条路边可以遇到任务npc卡西瓦 对话触发"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b1454a1bd10ff226363384bb9c99e92abbb8a402.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"任务需要费罗龙的鳞片 也就是雷龙材料 在地图下方 有个乌拉伊特湖 就是每天雷龙的出生点"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/555acf0ff2260d9a0da7a22c622abab84340a502.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"用篝火每天5点起床用远程弓箭射击龙的身体 就会掉落费罗龙的鳞片"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/d04eec260d9a310e2a305c9f31b842406bfea202.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/f367139a310e1799d7830f0dc9406afec214a302.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"获得龙鳞后 到勇气之泉 （任务接取位置的左上方遗迹）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/0cdb2f0e1799e92a8511f7f5e1fec314f0c5a002.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"把鳞片扔到水里就可以解锁神庙完成任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/304f0999e92abab802e9df4b4814f1c594eea102.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/16d8f72abab842402b5776a17ac595ee40c19e02.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"利特的兄弟岩任务","content":[{"type":"title","content":"利特的兄弟岩任务"},{"type":"text","content":"1.利特的兄弟岩在地图上的位置如图所示，兄弟岩在利利特特湖的西边"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/2gub2vvgo0l.png"},{"type":"text","content":"2.在兄弟岩这里找到奇尔，并和它对话，领取【利特的兄弟岩】神庙挑战任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/dgxunl3sknw.png"},{"type":"text","content":"3.根据和奇尔的对话，前往利特村找到庚珂，对话得知它要吃干煎三文鱼"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/l2viay143lv.png"},{"type":"text","content":"4.前往利特村的商店这里，找到格里戈莉，对话得到山羊黄油"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/kc4tin0o21f.png"},{"type":"text","content":"5.对话了解二姐在村子口的小池塘"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/vzwl5tt5mpj.png"},{"type":"text","content":"6.在村子口的小池塘这里找到二姐珂茨，对话得到生命三文鱼"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/q2bm5mcn3yf.png"},{"type":"text","content":"7.同时了解到大姐在利特村的最高处"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/ytup45ekvoj.png"},{"type":"text","content":"8.图中箭头指向的地方就是大姐所在的地方"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/znan25oedgh.png"},{"type":"text","content":"9.在利特村高处找到大姐娜楠"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/ofkw4klhjjy.png"},{"type":"text","content":"10.对话得到塔邦挞小麦"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/01t3gwewb2k.png"},{"type":"text","content":"11.然后回到庚珂这里，用获得的材料制作出生命干煎三文鱼"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/3wdm3l5fese.png"},{"type":"text","content":"12.将干煎三文鱼给庚珂吃"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/vydi2xdorrb.png"},{"type":"text","content":"13.然后再次前往兄弟岩，看到五只小鸟都到齐了"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/2xqtsphg5sm.png"},{"type":"text","content":"14.然后找到奇尔，和它对话，得知后面的柱子就是兄弟岩"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/4m3gayjoyyn.png"},{"type":"text","content":"15.奇尔赠送克洛格团扇"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/oc4cvqrjggi.png"},{"type":"text","content":"16.用克洛格团扇扇兄弟岩里的石头，先扇四根柱子的岩石"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/d4pf5guwxg1.png"},{"type":"text","content":"17.然后是五根柱子的岩石"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/fz1izsf2qon.png"},{"type":"text","content":"18.第三个是三根柱子"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/akkofxgr2uz.png"},{"type":"text","content":"19.第四个是一根柱子的"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/4k5b4ti5bjq.png"},{"type":"text","content":"20.第五个是两根柱子的"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/mi1czgfojbb.png"},{"type":"text","content":"21.按照顺序扇完之后就开启了神庙，完成了【利特的兄弟岩】"},{"type":"image","content":"https://www.alidown.com/d/file/titlepic/20230813/lz2p4z2fzup.png"}]},{"name":"探索拉聂尔山的宝贝(吉塔·萨米神庙)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"探索拉聂尔山的宝贝(吉塔·萨米神庙)"},{"type":"text","content":"探索拉聂尔山的宝贝是智慧之泉的神庙试炼任务,完成可以解锁智慧之泉的吉塔萨米神庙"},{"type":"text","content":"任务地点在拉聂尔山的山顶"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/d695563104ebf6a75329399effee1c324a184fbf.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"在山顶的智慧之泉有一个被盖侬污染的聂尔龙  第一次遇到就会触发这个任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/49701aebf6a75f0f8f0dcf5b97324b18502c4cbf.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/05aae8a75f0f822b7ac8a787c018512c8df14dbf.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/f7e6410f822b74ee1314f0adda2c8cf1d9a74abf.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"任务需要我们先清除龙身上的魔眼 使用远程类的弓箭射击魔眼即可"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/5e4e9c2b74ee1c325b3eea9907f1d8a727334bbf.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/994f412043715fdb7b06028f468920c5270f8cbf.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"射击后龙会飞起逃跑 只要乘着山上的气流滑翔射击 把所有的魔眼清除 龙就会恢复原状"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/5e615d715fdb3620f71c763cabc5260f89358dbf.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/423041db3620b93a82af9b70ad0f8835dc8a8abf.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/5e9a2820b93acd8970e39dba0335dd8a58de8bbf.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3761a73acd8920c577293380568a59de440788bf.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"恢复后 回到智慧之泉 再次射击一下聂尔龙 就可以获得龙鳞"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b87bd38920c5260fda13663fd2de4507890189bf.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ccc83ec5260f88358eace26bce078801397086bf.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/2184380f8835dd8a0df8feb203013870d44187bf.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"把龙鳞放到水中就可以解锁吉塔萨米神庙 完成任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/274e9635dd8a59de102133b4b370d5413b8c84bf.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/8974c38a59de4507de2783c55e413a8ca70885bf.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"神庙里的宝箱可以直接打开获得冰雪枪（年轻的武器迷任务需要的武器）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a9338a1fbee434da8578f196f271fe1d97d8e4bf.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"两杆枪野兽(米兹·耀神庙)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"两杆枪野兽(米兹·耀神庙)"},{"type":"text","content":"两杆枪野兽是游戏中的一个神庙试炼任务，完成后可以解锁米兹耀神庙"},{"type":"text","content":"任务接取位置如下"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/c8373cbc7dc5cf679c2362f38e96b814f5d026d6.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"到任务位置，可以看到任务npc卡西瓦，对话后就可以接取任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/30601b6104a355e976d25f62d22ae3efe17868d6.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/04201aa355e983ae1eabee9f68efe078153169d6.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"在草原里有很多雄鹿，我们需要穿着夜行衣，在草丛潜行慢慢靠近 "},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/05e24be983aee8d7ae56545a6b781431deb666d6.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/54a89daee8d7592a1b9357cd9f31dfb6336c67d6.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"潜行到屁股附近就可以骑上去驯服"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/82eff6d7592ae3ef1904a38454b6326c566664d6.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"驯服后骑着走到神庙的机关上，就可以解锁米兹耀神庙"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/e996472ae3efe078ee4d6803b96c576698cf65d6.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/586bfdefe078143124ca85d9dc6699cf035362d6.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"御风拓路者(希尤塔神庙)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"御风拓路者(希尤塔神庙)"},{"type":"text","content":"御风拓路者是一个神庙试炼任务，完成可以解锁希尤塔神庙 "},{"type":"text","content":"任务在拉聂耳草原触发"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b87bd38920c5260fde486a3fd2de4507890189d6.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"到草原可以看到npc扎西卡 对话触发任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ccc83ec5260f88358af7ee6bce078801397086d6.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"这个任务很简单 在边上的湖中有很多石洞 只需要把洞中的石头炸开就可以了"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/2184380f8835dd8a01a3f2b203013870d44187d6.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/c33acc828689a1461ecc594cf4bd4c7c35b334d7.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"如图 炸开三个石洞后 就可以使气流通过"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/d3c39889a146b7b14484c808c77c34b33d4135d7.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/87c8bf46b7b1eef9d4c0fbc9bfb33c4132ba32d7.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a007a9b1eef97fbde0018306b74133bad24133d7.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"然后站在中间的巨石上顺着气流飘到机关上 就可以完成任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b6f0f0f97fbd4c7c99ce8bf4b8bad341027d30d7.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/efb861bd4c7c34b3923c840f5841037de03731d7.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/7efc527c34b33c419cc764f4887de137c8762ed7.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/4d3d2ab33c4133ba633cb4c86a37c97623bc2fd7.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"解锁的神庙叫希尤塔神庙"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/35f2224133bad341b2005682427622bc7cc52cd7.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"英杰祭祀诗(达·基基神庙)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"英杰祭祀诗(达·基基神庙)"},{"type":"text","content":"英杰祭祀诗 是一个神庙试炼任务 需要我们找到祭祀之枪 来解锁村后瀑布下的机关 解锁达基基神庙"},{"type":"text","content":"任务触发是在卓拉领地的右侧的亭子游爷墨上和粉色小孩对话（应该是完成神兽任务才可以触发）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/c6b994775ddd884c2a3860916cef28066a01f6c8.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ba274f598540102aec0a5711b142a07aa110c57f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"和去后山的路上的老人对话可以获得线索 需要找到祭祀之枪"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a44e8afc508c9bce0c8ac5c1d6dd884ce44afac8.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"触发任务后 在领地下面的湖边可怕涛以用磁力找到祭祀之枪"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/51cd85cec7f88a7790afc7fa6e4a2f27e6eff8c8.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"用磁力可以吸上岸获得"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/7c84d1672b5fd546027fd1a77fd0b503c9d2247c.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"之后民裹下图位置，可以发现机关"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3bcdb808a50f94fc99fed4784cf88a775cddfcc8.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"用米法给林克的衣服爬上瀑布，飞到空中"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/8b3643dd884ce54aff55a859a3066b0193ddf7c8.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/5c9c964ce54a2f27369d67b0e00192dd3240f4c8.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"滑翔瞄准机关使用落地斩击，攻击到机关解锁达基基神庙完成任务  "},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/d400248ca608a50f5c8e1f3a10cec7f88b77ffc8.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/054056fe1e425d6b2f38209a11883913e9e5007c.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/de9bfa3b3b86022176befae5d8bbf82065fb727c.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"两个环(希·达哥兹神庙)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"两个环(希·达哥兹神庙)"},{"type":"text","content":"神庙位置 在桥边上"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/95bd4e8c9bcec7f81267de68034ce54a2e27fba5.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/e40b3127e7ef2806f4111168b840b6f39087f2a5.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"到位置可以看到那个无处不在的任务npc 对话获得两个环的神庙任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b7b28f87031c99c009ec6233af2fa872951feda5.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"在里面有两个环的洞孔朝着一边"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/955ea0e434daf05ee433fac4751d96d81919e5a5.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"只要蹲在一个环上 再瞄准放箭穿过另一个环就可以解锁神庙"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/19587f20a7cd0c6e4de28106fed7997bbaf4dda5.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"神庙里的机关也很简单 只要踩机关把珠子滚到洞里就可以打开门"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/983aa5f4da5872da6359e2ba0056ad042f68d4a5.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"这里面有个宝箱 需要飞到洞边上 拐角就可以看到"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/8a17b3042e6817e992f18d4dd356d53da924cea5.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/50a010f85856d53d6f345b5c47d2bb665059caa5.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"红月之夜(米达·罗基神庙)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"米达·罗基神庙 红月之夜"},{"type":"text","content":"这个神庙非常猎奇"},{"type":"text","content":"图中位置接取任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/e09173e89a61862520e2475d3b04541bd00faaca.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b1454a1bd10ff2266aebb8bb9c99e92abbb8a4ca.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"到地方在大蘑菇上有个鸟人，对话获得任务红月之夜"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/16d8f72abab84240078f4aa17ac595ee40c19eca.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/94af5fc1b727ac5372f918992ecadce8914899ca.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"这个任务需要在红月下完成（一般接到任务等到晚上就一定是红月），在鸟人脚下有个机关在红月时会亮起"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a48bc2e8904800fc0d8611bbd42043715edb93ca.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"此时就是非常厉害的设定了 需要无障碍接触月光 也就是把身上的衣服都脱掉，就可以解锁神庙"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/5e615d715fdb3620394b443cabc5260f89358dca.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"神庙是个打守护者的 可以获得最高级守护着武器"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/2184380f8835dd8adfafccb203013870d44187ca.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"绝壁花纹(基哈乌神庙)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"绝壁花纹(基哈乌神庙)"},{"type":"text","content":"绝壁花纹是个隐藏的神庙试炼任务完成可以解锁基哈乌神庙"},{"type":"text","content":"任务在塔邦达大桥驿站。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/1d735518512c8cf1102b2080c384cde34a2c4623.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"在驿站门口的山崖上有个眺望远方的npc。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/27725684cde34b2c9b627dcc0d0e7c75e4f44323.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"对话触发任务。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/7d34fbf4fcf5ee0dee42ac64f96b0ce264e7ba23.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/64a62a0f647814236235708daac2bbd6e0d0b223.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"任务在格鲁德山顶的崖壁上。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/2083a5d6e1d06de878ed8096ca93cee8b104ac23.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"到位置可以看到巨大闪电壁画中间有个机关 只要用闪电箭射中机关就可以解锁神庙。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/555acf0ff2260d9ada82112a622abab84340a523.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"这个神庙叫基哈乌神庙，里面可以直接开宝箱获得一颗钻石 。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/16d8f72abab842409a72c5a77ac595ee40c19e23.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"想见见守护者(希塔塔恩科神庙)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"想见见守护者(希塔塔恩科神庙)"},{"type":"text","content":"想见见守护者是一个神庙试炼任务，完成可解锁希塔塔恩科神庙"},{"type":"text","content":"任务位置在马神泉边上的海岸。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/95bd4e8c9bcec7f8f9e4f568034ce54a2e27fb28.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"到位置可以看到一个npc抱着机关球在陶醉。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/51cd85cec7f88a77294e20f96e4a2f27e6eff828.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"上去索要机关球 就可以触发任务 任务需要我们拍三张守护者的照片跟她换。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/9a8fd9f88a775dddfddf4dffa427e7ef2906f928.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/cd93a56651598540b8b9ac57b5a23a42a17ac428.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"这个三个守护者很容易找到，小守护者在神庙可以发现。 "},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ba274f598540102aad719617b142a07aa110c528.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"飞行的和爬行的守护者在海拉鲁城堡附近有很多。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/50189b40102a04e2943192f72b7aa010bd33c228.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/84010e2a04e23ea291d108cf2b10bc33ed38c328.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"找到并拍照后回去给npc看就可以获得机关球了 。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/116b1ae23ea23a420ce908a53733ec3835bbc028.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"把球抬到机关中心就可以解锁希塔塔恩科神庙 完成试炼。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/05a320a23a42a07a0d831486673834bb18efc128.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3fe32442a07aa01012a0448dbfbb19efa35f3e29.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"最初的试炼(乔卡席神庙)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"最初的试炼"},{"type":"text","content":"最初的试炼是克洛格的神庙试炼之一，完成可以解锁达乔卡席神庙"},{"type":"text","content":"任务位置在 克洛格森林 德库树前左上方的通道"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/1d735518512c8cf1ce769e86c384cde34a2c466a.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"德库树前面一共有四个通道通往森林的四个角落 这个任务在左上角的通道 可以遇到任务npc 对话就可以触发任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/4a594f2c8cf1d8a731e2f03146e34b2c57ee476a.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/506d92f1d8a7263350557556c02c56ee7a7f446a.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"接取任务后 在前方草丛有个呀哈哈 我们需要尾随在他身后 偷偷潜行跟随他 直到找到神庙  被发现任务就失败了"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/8db0c6a726334884d432f399ddee7b7f870e456a.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"跟随的方向会有很多潜行草 可以借此辨别方向"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/d9e638334884cde351fdee5bf07f860e7d75426a.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"在跟随到一个枯树干时 注意要躲避一下 因为呀哈哈会突然往回跑 "},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/27725684cde34b2c4d3fc3ca0d0e7c75e4f4436a.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"枯树干再往前走 会有一只狼 记住要提前杀掉 否则进入战斗状态 也会被呀哈哈发现"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/340e4eb8b43ea8db919b4287189c2cf7deb2166b.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"遇到狼后再往前走一段路就可以发现神庙完成试炼"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/51f9aa3ea8db574a3de32b29a7f7dfb2dd19176b.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"黑暗的试炼(基托瓦瓦伊神庙)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"黑暗的试炼(基托瓦瓦伊神庙)"},{"type":"text","content":"黑暗的试炼是一个神庙试炼任务，完成可以解锁基托瓦瓦伊神庙"},{"type":"text","content":"任务位置在死亡之山左侧的德依布朗遗迹"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/116b1ae23ea23a4201a113a53733ec3835bbc070.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/777f3fc2bbd6e1d0593529d40d254193cfe8af76.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"进入这个遗迹就可以触发任务  任务需要我们在黑暗中找到机关球解锁神庙"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/2083a5d6e1d06de8afbc3590ca93cee8b104ac76.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"使用火箭蓄力 不发射 可以当火把用 "},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ba97ffd06de89a61b0f8f22645e8b004551bad76.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"走到遗迹里面会发现一个独眼巨人 在黑暗中他的眼睛非常明亮 只需要射击眼睛他就会停下来让你近身攻击"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/e09173e89a618625764e7d5d3b04541bd00faa76.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"击杀后就会掉落机关球 把球抬到机关中心 就可以解锁神庙了"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/6ca9846186254193f63503b1df1bd10ff326ab76.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/9b2098254193cee889d9e7ae5a0ff2260c9aa876.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"神庙进去无需再次解谜 可以直接打开宝箱（古代核心） 过关"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/87645f93cee8b0046ec662ba79260d9a300ea976.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"操控力的试炼(库恩希达吉神庙)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"操控力的试炼"},{"type":"text","content":"操控力的试炼是克洛格的神庙试炼之一,完成可以解锁库恩希达吉神庙"},{"type":"text","content":"任务在 克洛格森林 德库树前左下方的通道"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/46315818dfdae43bd3b1ba94c457935652bb748d.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"在通道的入口的石头上可以发现npc 对话接取任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/4759c1dae43b3b86eb16f7e2185653bbf920758d.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/de9bfa3b3b860221a5602be3d8bbf82065fb728d.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"任务需要我们开着电磁之力，找出镶着铁球的树。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/e57a258602214f577861eb0e732064fb970b738d.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3ac71c214f579356bf8c4095effb960b3021708d.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"途中会发现一块铁盾牌。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/03605157935653bb1517dc4e1d0b31210461718d.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"盾牌边的树下还有碑文，阅读后控制盾牌送到树干里。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/4e168d5653bbf8208acc2ebeba21056105a36e8d.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/92174dbbf82064fb793c89948e6104a354e96f8d.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"之后在湖边的树干中可以发现一个宝箱。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/486884883913e8e50dd61509352f477047187d92.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/9bc92713e8e5ecee4f84069acc704618deda7a92.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"把宝箱吸到帆船上，用船送到对岸。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3852f6e5eceeadbc5d17ffc5cd18dfdae53b7b92.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"再把宝箱吸到对岸的树干中就可以完成试炼。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/e9a4f2eeadbcbe2fa348fead54dae43b3a867892.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/edafb3bcbe2f4770a320676f6f3b3b8603217992.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"不燃烧的试炼(库恩希达吉神庙)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"不燃烧的试炼(库恩希达吉神庙)"},{"type":"text","content":"不燃烧的试炼是克洛格森林里的一个神庙试炼任务 需要我们通过试炼解锁神庙"},{"type":"text","content":"任务接取在克洛格森林里"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ed792abb19efa25fbce769ce59828689a0463b49.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"在德库树前右上方的通道可以遇到任务npc 对话就可以触发任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/35fa07efa25f0c14738879370d89a146b6b13849.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/18aebc5f0c14c27b60712d3c2a46b7b1eff93949.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"接取任务后自动开始 需要用指定的武器穿过怪物看守的道路找到神庙（ 在接取任务时需要有三个装备空缺 来装备任务武器 ）\n\n刚开始只要往前跑遇到蓝色史莱姆往右边的箱子方向跑"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a31e1214c27bd282357a0af33cb1eef97ebd3649.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/0d55dc7bd282868915b51c0465f97fbd4d7c3749.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"使用炸弹快速炸开木箱"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/c33acc828689a1460242454cf4bd4c7c35b33449.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"继续前进可以看到燃烧的蝙蝠 蝙蝠会点燃地上的草 可以使用火焰产生的气流飞跃沼泽"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/d3c39889a146b7b1580ad408c77c34b33d413549.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/87c8bf46b7b1eef9c84ee7c9bfb33c4132ba3249.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"前方有两个沼泽 可以使用冰块爬过去 通过沼泽就可以看见神庙完成任务"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a007a9b1eef97fbdf48f9f06b74133bad2413349.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a1780d1fceecd3d9888659716799594305010849.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/125ed0ecd3d969751037472cd243040149fe0949.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"雷鸣的试炼(托雅萨神庙)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"雷鸣的试炼"},{"type":"text","content":"雷鸣的试炼是一个神庙试炼任务，完成可开启托雅萨神庙"},{"type":"text","content":"任务位置在海拉鲁丘陵 上面的雷之台地"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3b8fb4d7726b0ce241d18ebaef781423bfb9b68f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"可以在丘陵之塔直接飞过去"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ab966c6b0ce265e71139decd9f23beb9773eb78f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"进入台地就会自动接取这个任务台地里有个废墟 柱子上有红色的球 需要需要我们先爬上去（台地里身带金属武器会被雷击 雨天攀爬技巧 4步1跳 可以避免滑下来）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/732a12e265e7340f424eae9635b9763e20c2b48f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"爬上去后 使用时间静止配合连续打击 可以把球撞到中间的高地"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/0da37be7340f64783315040cfd3e21c2bad6b58f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/64a62a0f64781423968fcc8baac2bbd6e0d0b28f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"之后爬上高地把红球放入有红色柱子的机关中"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/354e7a781423beb95f089b7730d6e1d06ce8b38f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"紫色的球 就在紫色柱子边上"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/65390a23beb9763e0bf401636ad06de89b61b08f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"绿色的球 需要用弓箭 在柱子上射下来（从背面射可以直接掉到机关里）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/1562a0b9763e21c290e05b65e6e89a618725b18f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"还有个黄色的球 在台地另一端 需要爬上很高的柱子 再时间静止 打飞到高台上"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/dda98e4800fc77f7d238e595c8715fdb3720908f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/91091efc77f7980e1416f9c4d4db3620b83a918f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"把三个球都放到机关 就可以解锁托雅萨神庙"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/01bd69f7980e5f200f47e56ebd20b93acc898e8f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"野外的试炼(库古·齐德神庙)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"野外的试炼(库古·齐德神庙)"},{"type":"text","content":"野外的试炼也是游戏的支线任务之一，需要我们在荒岛上找到三个球并放入机关中来解锁神庙"},{"type":"text","content":"任务位置在地图的最右下角的孤岛"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/bbf95c406afec314b1f32d5bcac1b727ad539c8f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"进入荒岛 就可以触发任务  触发后我们的武器衣服都会消失 就像低配版的剑之试炼"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/430174fec314f1c5d4d8f9743c27ac5307889d8f.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"岛上有两个小山  每个上面都有机关和怪物  第一座山上 我们先清理机关上的铁箱子"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/6a408cdd3340b6f3ffb0bba912c0affce086ee8c.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"在山下有个独眼巨人  脖子上有机关球 我们可以直接飞到他脖子上偷走机关球"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/939c2d40b6f391876c2b217524fce186252fef8c.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3201a8f39187031ce9f717496a86242fa972ec8c.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"再按着小路上山放入机关"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b7b28f87031c99c0decb5933af2fa872951fed8c.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/90c61d1c99c0affc93b19c9a2372941fbfe4ea8c.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"另一座山上怪物比较多 击杀后 在机关边的木架上就可以找到机关球"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/025d87c0affce186571810c71f1fbee435daeb8c.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"这个机关被石头盖住了 需要用时间静止住石头蓄力攻击 把它打飞"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/9881b1fce186242fdc452caa35e434daf15ee88c.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/aebdff86242fa872e1280651bfdaf05e4b23e98c.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"第三个球在怪物巢穴的最顶端 获得后 需要运到小岛最上方的河岸"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/e0c73a2fa872941fc8d38c6f7b5e4a237871e68c.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/256eb672941fbee443ed48ebc1237971ff1de78c.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"我们需要把球放进水中的机关里 可以把球扔进入水 再用冰块顶起来  这样就可以把球运到机关里了"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/87c8bf46b7b1eef9d58af4c9bfb33c4132ba328d.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a007a9b1eef97fbde74b8c06b74133bad241338d.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"三个机关激活后 就可以解锁神庙完成任务了 神庙里有个宝箱 可以获得金卢比"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b6f0f0f97fbd4c7c988484f4b8bad341027d308d.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/efb861bd4c7c34b391768b0f5841037de037318d.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"闪电开启的试炼(丘卡纳塔神庙)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"闪电开启的试炼(丘卡纳塔神庙)"},{"type":"text","content":"闪电开启的试炼是一个神庙试炼，完成可以解锁 丘卡纳塔神庙"},{"type":"text","content":"任务触发点在克拉尔湖"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/df087f0f8b56ad04a45cad5cdae10ef85956d089.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"湖边的山顶上我们可以遇到任务npc卡西瓦 "},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/604e9556ad042e689cddeb5485f85856d43dd189.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/8a17b3042e6817e9ddd5b44dd356d53da924ce89.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"和他对话听他的诗歌 了解需要打开前面的巨石"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ac45306817e951e183cce2e35e3da824d9e9cf89.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"我们先爬上石头顶（注意不要装备金属物品）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/2f2909e951e10ef8d6626f882324d8e9cdd2cc89.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"在石头顶 扔下一个铁质武器  就可以引雷打碎石块"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/16a84fe10ef858565a09129153e9ccd2ba66cd89.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/50a010f85856d53d3810625c47d2bb665059ca89.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"石块里面就是丘卡纳塔神庙 进去可以直接打开宝箱完成试炼"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/0fb94656d53da82449dd7667306651598440cb89.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/4e168d5653bbf82088cf2cbeba21056105a36e8e.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]}]},{"name":"其他","key":"huiyi","content":[{"name":"旷野之息 13个回忆点位置在哪？回忆点位置介绍","icon":"cuIcon-light text-red","content":[{"type":"title","content":"旷野之息 回忆点位置在哪？回忆点位置介绍"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/DAjtghbrEhDopgk.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"回忆点位置"},{"type":"text","content":"1、第一个，祭奠场遗迹，回忆点的画家可能在森林驿站"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/LIcfWSbrEhDoooq.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/AYPozYbrEhDonvg.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"2、第二个，科摩罗池塘，回忆点的画家在河畔驿站"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/kYMtbxbrEhDomzz.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/YMAabebrEhDomea.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"3、第三个，古代石柱群，回忆点的画家在塔邦达大桥驿站。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/YBRhsFbrEhDolmg.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/sWRrecbrEhDoktE.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"4、第四个，卡拉卡拉集市，回忆点的画家在格鲁德峡谷驿站"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/mdQobdbrEhDojEF.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/BpgSufbrEhDojlu.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"5、第五个，奥尔汀峡谷，回忆点的画家在鼓隆城。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/HfqAocbrEhDoixF.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/bvUQfnbrEhDoiei.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"6、第六个，巴奇平原，回忆点的画家在玛丽塔驿站。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/HfqAocbrEhDoixF.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/bvUQfnbrEhDoiei.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"7、第七个，西哈特尔，回忆点的画家在高原驿站。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/OxEnkQbrEhDohnl.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/xLpAVJbrEhDogvp.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"8、第八个海拉鲁城堡，回忆点的画家在沃托里村。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/TWWcxPbrEhDofBr.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/UmkeQdbrEhDofeo.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"9、第九个，力量之泉，回忆点的画家在阿卡莱驿站"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/VkKmsObrEhDoepB.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/mqCYorbrEhDodxB.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"10、第十个，撒丁公园遗迹，回忆点的画家在平原外围的驿站。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/LuySkubrEhDocDD.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/uVlIyxbrEhDoclx.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"11、第十一个，拉聂尔山回忆点在卡卡利科村往东走。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/gUQdtsbrEhDobuh.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/hedHxhbrEhDoavf.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"12、第十二个，海拉鲁平原。回忆点的画家在湿地驿站"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/ehNHgVbrEhDoaan.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/mqCYorbrEhDodxB.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"13、第十三个，也是百年前那场大战的结局点。触发地点就在双子驿站后面那堆守护者中间。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/cMkCBPbrEhDnFgF.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/jQjeHibrEhDnEoo.jpg!a-3-854x.jpg"}]},{"name":"Switch及旷野之息基础知识","icon":"cuIcon-light text-red","content":[{"type":"title","content":"Switch及旷野之息基础知识"},{"type":"title","content":"(操作说明)"},{"type":"text","content":"左摇杆:   移动\n右摇杆:    视角操作\n按下左摇杆:    切换站立/蹲下\n按下右摇杆:    使用望远镜\n A:    调查/互动\n B:    加速行动\n X:    跳跃\n Y:    攻击\n L:    使用道具\n R:    投掷武器\n ZL:    锁定\n ZR:    使用弓箭\n →:    切换武器\n ←:    切换盾牌\n ↑:    切换希卡之石道具\n ↓:    吹口哨"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/FnjshCbsnpegktC.jpg!a-3-800x.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"(界面说明)"},{"type":"text","content":"1：体力槽\n2：当前使用的道具/装备\n3：当前精力\n4：温度、音量、当前时间与天气\n5：小地图"},{"type":"image","content":"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/HeIPFObsnpegjFF.jpg!a-3-800x.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"(内容说明)"},{"type":"text","content":"精力：在奔跑、攀爬以及游泳等动作的时候会使用精力，如果精力用完会进入疲惫状态，疲惫状态无法奔跑、攀爬以及游泳。"},{"type":"text","content":"攀爬：对着墙壁就可以攀爬，按X可以跳跃一段距离，速度更快，但是消耗精力更多。"},{"type":"text","content":"游泳：可以在水面游泳，但是不能潜水。按X可以向前加速冲刺一段距离，消耗较多精力，如果在水里精力为0就会淹死。"},{"type":"text","content":"炎热：不停损失HP、木质装备耐久会减少、食物可以自动加热。可以穿着防热装备或料理来抵抗炎热。"},{"type":"text","content":"寒冷：不停损失HP、动物死后直接变成冻肉。可以穿着防冻装备或料理来抵抗寒冷。"},{"type":"text","content":"雷雨：无法生火、攀爬困难、如果装备金属装备可能会被雷劈。"},{"type":"text","content":"料理：把食物扔进锅里可以调和出相应的料理。"},{"type":"text","content":"攻击方式：普通攻击（轻按Y）、蓄力攻击（长按Y）、投掷攻击（R）"},{"type":"text","content":"武器分类：单手武器、双手武器、长手武器、功能性武器、弓箭。"},{"type":"text","content":"单手武器：攻速快，可以当匕首一样丢出。"},{"type":"text","content":"双手武器：攻击高，攻速慢，蓄力可以大风车旋风斩。"},{"type":"text","content":"长手武器：攻击距离远，威力小，蓄力攻击类似《王者荣耀》赵云的连环突刺。"},{"type":"text","content":"功能性武器：用于解谜，实战几乎无战斗力。"},{"type":"text","content":"弓箭：远程攻击，射出的是抛物线，可以使用陀螺仪辅助瞄准。"},{"type":"text","content":"武器耐久：所有武器都有耐久度，如果用完就会损坏无法使用，不可以修复，所以多寻找强力武器就显得尤为重要了。"},{"type":"text","content":"属性：游戏中有冰、火、雷三种属性攻击。"},{"type":"text","content":"冰属性：冰属性可以秒杀火属性敌人，也可以将敌人冻结"},{"type":"text","content":"火属性：火属性可以秒杀冰属性敌人，可以对木柴攻击生火"},{"type":"text","content":"雷属性：雷属性可以麻痹敌人，攻击冰、金属类型敌人可以造成额外伤害。"},{"type":"text","content":"盾牌：按L进行防御。"},{"type":"text","content":"盾滑：按L再按X，跳起后，按A可以踩盾滑行，滑行时不消耗体力，但是消耗盾的耐久。"},{"type":"text","content":"盾反：按住L防御，在敌人攻击自己的瞬间按A可以将对方攻击弹开，如果对方是近战会造成硬直，如果对方是远程会把弹道弹飞。"},{"type":"text","content":"偷袭：在潜行状态下，接近敌人背后，可以按Y进行偷袭，会造成8倍伤害并会造成很大的硬直效果，所以能偷袭尽量偷袭敌人。"}]},{"name":"大神3❤️无伤刷双马","icon":"cuIcon-video text-red","content":[{"type":"title","content":"大神3❤️无伤刷双马"},{"type":"text","content":"转载的dy一个大神3❤️无伤刷双马,感觉很帅！"},{"type":"video","error":true,"content":"export/UzFfAgtgekIEAQAAAAAA9JwAVo0WjgAAAAstQy6ubaLX4KHWvLEZgBPEtaJ0d1MPVZeKzNPgMJombGpjJBLYQc3jrJGvWsMQ"},{"type":"text","content":"👉作者主页：https://v.douyin.com/iUhUvY4s/ 2@7.com :3pm"}]},{"name":"塞尔达怎么获取防寒服？","icon":"cuIcon-light text-red","content":[{"type":"title","content":"塞尔达怎么获取防寒服？"},{"type":"text","content":"塞尔达防寒服获取流程"},{"type":"text","content":"去到如图所示位置，食材准备好就去找老人的屋子，在时光之神殿往南走，找到后进去桌子上有本书和几个距鬼新暖暖草果。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/03605157935653bb72247f431d0b31210561715c.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"然获敏后选择消磨到晚上，老人就会出来，跟老人交谈，跟他说最近做了些兼宋料理，然后给他，他就会给你防寒服了。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3ac71c214f579356dabfe398effb960b3121705c.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"塞尔达如何恢复武器耐久","content":[{"type":"title","content":"塞尔达如何恢复武器耐久"},{"type":"text","content":"分享下塞尔达如何恢复武器耐久。"},{"type":"text","content":"在游戏袋子里，找到弹簧锤，然后点击装备弹簧锤，弹簧锤可以修复其他武器耐久度。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/35fa07efa25f0c14356eb7350d89a146b6b138ad.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"然后在袋子中，找到武器耐久度快要没有的武器，点击装备。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/a151a233ec3834bbedfac7e88714c27bd3823dad.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"接着让角色使用弹簧锤进行跳劈，砸一下地面。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/bd72f23834bb19ef574a69a3497bd28287893aad.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"然后再打开袋子，这样武器耐久度就恢复了。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ed792abb19efa25ffa01a7cc59828689a0463bad.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"克洛格(呀哈哈)兑换地点","content":[{"type":"title","content":"呀哈哈兑换地点"},{"type":"text","content":"呀哈哈在《塞尔达传说荒野之息》中，算得上最“麻烦”的收集要素了，数量多，分布广。这里总结下呀哈哈的兑换地点"},{"type":"text","content":"克洛格果实商人：伯库林 克洛格兑换，需要完成“重要的沙果”迷你挑战（克洛格果实共有900颗）"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/586bfdefe0781431b5a97ad8dc6699cf035362b7.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"第一次克洛格兑换地点：卡卡利科村路上 克洛格每次兑换的个数，逐渐递增，第一次1颗，第二次2颗，第二次3颗。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/031231632385e036908e0f5cb8e039723c035ab7.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"第二次克洛格兑换地点：河畔驿站旁边或者瓦哥.卡塔神庙旁边。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3fc72e486143d7d4342e4c5f7da75f0f832b50b7.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"武器袋、弓箭袋、盾牌袋都兑换需要441个克洛格。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/75af02324b18512c09ee9013ad334884cce349b7.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"第三次及其之后克洛格兑换地点：迷失森林里面（基耀.乌神庙的南边）。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/cca2552c56ee7b7f0b1134c16ef4fcf5ef0d41b7.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"塞尔达快速刷箭支方式一","content":[{"type":"title","content":"塞尔达快速刷箭支方式一"},{"type":"text","content":"塞尔达游戏里经常会遇到箭不够用的情况，下面介绍下塞尔达怎么刷箭。"},{"type":"text","content":"传送到小岛试炼的库古齐德神庙；"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/b955ead0b503c8d277d203fb498333bf3aef2181.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/92dd32f7dfb2dc198e001fae95def4dca1391081.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"去神庙右面一个单独的小岛；"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/6834ecc4ec995943482d0c4b95425d6b05d10481.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/9bc92713e8e5eceefb90fa9acc704618deda7a81.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"水池中有个铁宝箱；"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/de9bfa3b3b860221117bd7e3d8bbf82065fb7281.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"选中磁铁，把宝箱吸上来，打开，得到木箭10支；"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/30601b6104a355e9eb82ac62d22ae3efe1786881.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/562787cf02532f6357a9a483699147e832e05c81.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/32a127723d03bbea42aa74fdea43d7d449315481.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/05aae8a75f0f822bf1c25887c018512c8df14d81.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"打开系统-保存；"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/cca2552c56ee7b7f172238c06ef4fcf5ef0d4181.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/65390a23beb9763e81eeff636ad06de89b61b081.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"打开系统-读取，读取刚刚的存档；"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/d04eec260d9a310eb9b5ad9f31b842406bfea281.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ad121888912ca5ca60c4d4fd8bfc77f7990e9481.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"退出系统菜单，发现宝箱刷新了，又可以得到10支箭，重复使用S/L大法就可以获得大量弓箭。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/3761a73acd8920c5ee23cc80568a59de44078881.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"}]},{"name":"塞尔达如何获取爆炸箭","content":[{"type":"title","content":"塞尔达如何获取爆炸箭"},{"type":"text","content":"塞尔达怎么获取爆炸箭，只需要几个简单的步骤"},{"type":"text","content":"首先我们需要打开地图查看自己的所在位置，位于【骷髅池塘】上方。\n"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/ba97ffd06de89a61c848da2b45e8b004551badc5.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"然后我们身处的这个地方是【正在下雨】的，可以看到树的下方【有小怪物】。\n"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/e09173e89a6186250efe55503b04541bd00faac5.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"接着我们【走进去】让小怪物看到并用【箭】射向我们。\n"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/6ca98461862541939e852bbcdf1bd10ff326abc5.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"最后因为正在下雨【爆炸箭不会爆炸】，我们可以捡起地上的【爆炸箭】放进袋子里。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/87645f93cee8b00406764ab779260d9a300ea9c5.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1%2Fformat%2Cf_auto%2Fquality%2Cq_80"},{"type":"text","content":"另外在这个地点附近刷Amiibo开宝箱，属性箭(比较大可能)会变成爆炸箭。"}]},{"name":"100%盾反守护者教程","icon":"cuIcon-video text-red","content":[{"type":"title","content":"100%盾反"},{"type":"video","error":true,"content":"export/UzFfAgtgekIEAQAAAAAAFREQAJgQQQAAAAstQy6ubaLX4KHWvLEZgBPE66JIfFQGA9GKzNPgMJqRlANULZ385y8Kqf9DEZen"},{"type":"text","content":"守护者的激光分成几个阶段："},{"type":"text","content":"1.寻找确定的目标，这时候，会有红外线在你身上摇摆并在身上有一个圈包着的红点。"},{"type":"text","content":"2.确定目标，这时候，红外线在你身上的圈不见了，然后声音越来越急促"},{"type":"text","content":"3.开始攻击，就是这个瞬间，你身上的那个红点不见了，红点消失后，按A，百分百成功！"},{"type":"image","content":"https://img1.ali213.net/glpic/2018/03/20/584_2018032012831184.jpg"}]},{"name":"盾反炸弹的小技巧","icon":"cuIcon-video text-red","content":[{"type":"title","content":"盾反炸弹的小技巧"},{"type":"text","content":"旷野之息盾反炸弹的小技巧\n利用盾反+炸弹打出超高伤害"},{"type":"video","error":true,"content":"export/UzFfAgtgekIEAQAAAAAAMUcLa-oBwQAAAAstQy6ubaLX4KHWvLEZgBPEk6IUEwRfHN2KzNPgMJqnXi8YQpyKilbXBROwOrKv"}]},{"name":"打人马的5种小技巧","icon":"cuIcon-video text-red","content":[{"type":"title","content":"打人马的5种小技巧"},{"type":"text","content":"打人马的5种小技巧\n塞尔达旷野之息攻略"},{"type":"video","error":true,"content":"export/UzFfAgtgekIEAQAAAAAAdjEwZfrJZgAAAAstQy6ubaLX4KHWvLEZgBPE7aJENAdxbN-KzNPgMJpfJTuUNgIbcC1md2pSvomr"}]},{"name":"迷宫篇之洛美岛","icon":"cuIcon-video text-red","extra":"内容来自百度-海鹤永不停息(https://mbd.baidu.com/newspage/data/dtlandingsuper?nid=dt_3946764570102565235)\n视频来自抖音-塞尔达月亮(https://v.douyin.com/iA5teu76/)","content":[{"type":"title","content":"迷宫篇之洛美岛"},{"type":"video","error":true,"content":"export/UzFfAgtgekIEAQAAAAAAaZ0gv5R3jQAAAAstQy6ubaLX4KHWvLEZgBPEk6IkJE98U6KKzNPgMJpnGCvemLFZtk-t9N0HNes5"},{"type":"text","content":"欢迎大家来到位于地图右上角的洛美岛迷宫"},{"type":"image","content":"https://s1.imagehub.cc/images/2024/11/12/0d08664251879ab6aae5a3a236a76699.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"新手朋友萌不要害怕，全宫共有守护者两名，一个不动一个瞎溜达；小蝙蝠若干，一打就没；电丘丘若干，有橡胶套比较方便没有就电一下也木事"},{"type":"text","content":"✨地上爬到顶耗费体力一圈多4/5圈（不跳跃）"},{"type":"text","content":"✨天上一共有四个飞行守护者 用炸弹箭打了三下都没掉血 建议躲着点不要打 打不过"},{"type":"text","content":"✨下雨爬墙小技能：向上爬四下然后跳跃 这是目前雨天爬墙距离最大的方式了 如果有鸟神兽技能最好"},{"type":"text","content":"✨神庙入口中间（黄色字体）荆棘烧掉爬上去就能拿火焰大剑"},{"type":"text","content":"✨神庙是祝福神庙 里面的宝箱是蛮族套装"},{"type":"text","content":"✨开完神庙后 神庙门口有一个气孔 跳下去是生锈的守护者窝（有装生锈的 如果穿英杰服或者用时停能看出来）进去之后它不会打你，直走拿到宝箱（钻石头套）之后五个守护者会揍你，建议立马传送到神庙，打不过（打得过估计也得被揍一下子）"},{"type":"text","content":"✨迷宫右边太穷了啥也没有 但是左边还是比较丰盛 总结下来全图共4个武器点 八个宝箱（也有可能每个人开出来的东西不完全一样）"},{"type":"text","content":""}]},{"name":"装备系列之古代兵装/Ancient","content":[{"type":"title","content":"装备系列之古代兵装/Ancient"},{"type":"text","content":"古代兵装的一套盔甲防御力非常高"},{"type":"text","content":"古代兵装的剑、枪、弓攻击力非常高"},{"type":"text","content":"古代兵装的弓箭，一箭就能让大部分敌人消失（就像放逐到异次元）。不过敌人也不会掉落素材或武器。（总之就是很强)"},{"type":"text","content":"当你在 Hateno / ハテノ村 完成主线任务，就会触发这个支线任务【Robbie’s Research / もう一人の研究者】。\n来到地图的东北角，找到第二个古代研究所。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://gmwiki.com/_media/wiki/zeldabotw/6.%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A31.jpg?cache="},{"type":"text","content":"和这里的老头儿【Robbie / ロベリー】对话，他会要求查看林克身上的伤口。脱下衣服让他查看后，再和他对话，就会触发传火的任务。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://gmwiki.com/_media/wiki/zeldabotw/6.%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A32.jpg?cache="},{"type":"text","content":"按照地图指示，来到蓝色火焰位置，一路传火回到研究所，点燃研究所外的炉子即可。方法和 Hateno / ハテノ村 一样。"},{"type":"text","content":"完成传火任务，可从【Robbie / ロベリー】处获得3支古代兵装·箭。"},{"type":"text","content":"之后和研究所里的人偶对话，就能购买古代兵装了。"},{"type":"text","content":"古代兵装系列的装备也不便宜，冒险过程中要积极收集守护者掉落的零件。守护者遗骸内会有不少这类零件。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://gmwiki.com/_media/wiki/zeldabotw/6.%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A33.jpg?cache="}]},{"name":"【大师模式 剑之试炼】-简介","content":[{"type":"title","content":"剑之试炼-简介"},{"type":"text","content":"“剑之试炼”就是一连串的试炼挑战。"},{"type":"text","content":"需获得大师剑后才能接受“剑之试炼”。"},{"type":"text","content":"进入试炼时，玩家不能携带任何装备、武器、道具，四个英杰能力也无法携带。炸弹、磁力、时间凝滞等符文能力当然还是有的。"},{"type":"text","content":"但你的血量和耐力继承在外面世界的数值，建议提升血量/耐力后再来挑战。"},{"type":"text","content":"吃料理获得的 Buff 在进入试炼时会保持。"},{"type":"text","content":"若中途退出或死亡，都需重第一层重新开始挑战。"},{"type":"text","content":"完成的试炼可以重复挑战。"},{"type":"text","content":"整个剑之试炼有三个阶段, 每个阶段都包含不同地理环境中数个楼层的连续战斗，并都以击倒所有敌人为最终目标。"},{"type":"text","content":"每完成一个阶段的试炼，大师剑的攻击力将上升10点，完成最后的试炼，大师剑的攻击力可达60。"},{"type":"text","content":"在挑战过程中被击倒的敌人不会掉落道具，但可以获得它们手持的武器装备。"},{"type":"text","content":"破坏的场景能生成相应的道具。"},{"type":"text","content":"隐藏在各层中的宝箱中有武器装备，而食材则只能通过破坏场景中的木桶木箱铁箱等来获取 。\n"},{"type":"title","content":"如何进入剑之试炼"},{"type":"text","content":"去地图北方的“korok forest”，就是获得大师剑的地方。将大师剑插回基座即可进入试炼。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://gmwiki.com/_media/wiki/zeldabotw/7.%E5%89%91%E4%B9%8B%E8%AF%95%E7%82%BC/%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B1.jpg"}]},{"name":"【大师模式 剑之试炼】- 初级阶段","content":[{"type":"title","content":"大师模式 剑之试炼-初级阶段"},{"type":"text","content":"“初始试炼只有12层分两个阶段，第1~6层为密林场景，第8~12层为水面场景；其中第6和第12层是boss战，第7层是整备层。"},{"type":"text","content":"准备"},{"type":"text","content":"升级了石板的技能，即炸弹，感应器，时停。练习无限背刺(偷袭怪物但怪物没死倒下后，走到怪物倒下时头朝的一方，怪物起身后又可以进行背刺)"},{"type":"text","content":"小技巧"},{"type":"text","content":"当你蹲下推动摇杆，如果推到底 蹲走会快些，但容易被怪物察觉。当你轻推摇杆时，会走的很慢，但是怪物不容易察觉。在大师模式剑之试炼中，要一直用轻推摇杆蹲走的方式进行背刺。"},{"type":"text","content":"第1层"},{"type":"text","content":"进去传送点正对的树上有鸟蛋"},{"type":"text","content":"调到炸弹，走过去把怪物引过来，它们全过来就丢炸弹炸散，然后找个最近的目标，交替丢炸弹炸死，另外两只也是如此。这关可以拿到斧子，12攻的生锈铁剑，生锈枪，盾牌和一些食材。其他可以不要。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://gmwiki.com/_media/wiki/zeldabotw/7.%E5%89%91%E4%B9%8B%E8%AF%95%E7%82%BC/%E5%88%9D1.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"第2层"},{"type":"text","content":"进去丢炸弹炸死火丘丘 "},{"type":"text","content":"跑到单独的哨兵台下，斧子砍木桶获得木箭，爬上台子把哥布林打下去，用炸弹交替炸死，获得弓。爬到对着台子哨兵的大树上，跳下树利用林克时间射死哨兵。爬到另一棵大树顶，等两只哥布林都背对你时，滑倒台子上，蹲下调出12攻的生锈铁剑进行背刺。记得拿上铁锤。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://gmwiki.com/_media/wiki/zeldabotw/7.%E5%89%91%E4%B9%8B%E8%AF%95%E7%82%BC/%E5%88%9D2.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"第3层"},{"type":"text","content":"场景前面和后面的墙上有宝箱"},{"type":"text","content":"炸弹炸丘丘，没啥讲的，离远点就行，主要是一定要拿宝箱。投掷斧子砸下来可获得火箭和回旋镖。"},{"type":"title","content":"第4层"},{"type":"text","content":"先从远处用箭将中间楼梯口的哥布林射掉，然后在边缘处蹲下从右边接近哥布林的营地，逐个击破。"},{"type":"text","content":"高台上的哥布林可以在营地的最高处用箭射杀，这样不会引爆上面的炸 药桶。"},{"type":"text","content":"也可以进去直接顺梯子爬上高台戳死哥布林，跳下林克时间射死哨兵。再次爬上高台，等最顶层的哥布林背对你时滑到台子上进行无限背刺，一路背刺下去，"},{"type":"image","content":"https://gmwiki.com/_media/wiki/zeldabotw/7.%E5%89%91%E4%B9%8B%E8%AF%95%E7%82%BC/%E5%88%9D3.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"第5层"},{"type":"text","content":"进去蹲下往左或者往右都行，走到树后面等着莫里布林背对你的时候‘时停’它。迅速跑到它的身后蹲下。等时停结束可以背刺，用士兵剑背刺。"},{"type":"text","content":"另一只也可以这样。如果时停背刺失败，可以时停后打死。解决掉两只莫里布林后继续蹲下走到骷髅头眼洞下方。弓箭射眼洞里的吊火，爆炸后的瞬间迅速爬上眼洞，跳下利用林克时间尽量爆 头射杀哥布林，然后解决剩余的敌人。完成后去捡到洞口的双手大棒。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://gmwiki.com/_media/wiki/zeldabotw/7.%E5%89%91%E4%B9%8B%E8%AF%95%E7%82%BC/%E5%88%9D4.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"第6层"},{"type":"text","content":"进去可以直接调出上炸弹炸掉它的右手，用上层获得的27攻大棒直接从它的后面爬到石头人的身上敲击矿石四下然后跳下，待它后仰后爬上去继续敲四下，如此反复。大棒坏了就用铁锤或者18攻的大棒。一定只能敲四下，被它后仰扔到地上就很麻烦。失误的话，就调出炸弹炸掉它的双手。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://gmwiki.com/_media/wiki/zeldabotw/7.%E5%89%91%E4%B9%8B%E8%AF%95%E7%82%BC/%E5%88%9D5.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"第7层"},{"type":"text","content":"进去蹲下过去捉精灵。捉到后砍树，准备几捆木材，掉下来的扇子也带上一把，火把也带上。搜集到的食材可以做出两级的攻击料理和防御料理，做的时候加入鸟蛋可以增加40秒左右的buff时间。其余食材可以自行搭配。"},{"type":"text","content":"右边是3个宝箱，宝箱后面有几个木箱，打破可获得弓箭等。烹饪点在左边，附近也能找到一些食材，树上有两个苹果水里有3条鱼，接下来的所有整备层大致都是这样的配置。"},{"type":"title","content":"第8层"},{"type":"text","content":"进去后用单手剑加时停解决掉趴着和射箭的蜥蜴。站在对岸水里造冰后先射死雷丘丘，站在冰上吸引到正对着你的那只黑蜥蜴，它过来的时候游回对岸，在岸上将其解决。如果背对你那只没有发现你，可以慢慢游过去背刺击杀。"},{"type":"text","content":"右上角传送点旁以及中间都有蜥蜴，左上角的水底里有宝箱。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://gmwiki.com/_media/wiki/zeldabotw/7.%E5%89%91%E4%B9%8B%E8%AF%95%E7%82%BC/%E5%88%9D6.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"第9层"},{"type":"text","content":"射死水里两只章鱼。然后还有一个雷法师，小心在水里被放出的雷球电到，在岸上用时间凝滞停住雷法师再攻击即可，如果停住后太高够不到可以用箭射，等时间凝滞结束，它会掉下来。"},{"type":"text","content":"左边有宝箱，需要用冰柱将它升起来。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://gmwiki.com/_media/wiki/zeldabotw/7.%E5%89%91%E4%B9%8B%E8%AF%95%E7%82%BC/%E5%88%9D8.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"第10层"},{"type":"text","content":"难点层，有三只强力的蜥蜴在桥的另一边 ，进入后立刻下水不要被蜥蜴发现，从桥底下游到蜥蜴的地方，没被发现的话还可以偷袭一个。"},{"type":"text","content":"之后可以用炸弹边不停转圈边把它们炸下水再用箭射它们"},{"type":"text","content":"这个过程中，如果有一只蜥蜴上岸，可以用时间凝滞，或用上一层拿到的雷法杖麻住它，再用其它武器攻击；如果多只蜥蜴上岸，就继续把它们炸下水。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://gmwiki.com/_media/wiki/zeldabotw/7.%E5%89%91%E4%B9%8B%E8%AF%95%E7%82%BC/%E5%88%9D9.jpg"},{"type":"title","content":"第11层"},{"type":"text","content":"如果体力不够游到对岸的话，可以用在第一层拿到的扇子乘木筏过去，左边在水里的石头围着有一个宝箱。"},{"type":"text","content":"木筏到了差不多的距离可以先解决一些用箭的哥布林然后再上岸，上去以后除了普通哥布林外，还有一个哥布林在第二层，一个高哥布林在最高层，用时间凝滞，再将它们打入水里即可，这一层的敌人掉水里会直接死亡。"},{"type":"text","content":"完成后右边高台上有一个金属宝箱（之前站着一个用箭的哥布林），可以用磁力吸过来。"},{"type":"title","content":"第12层"},{"type":"text","content":"独眼Boss，攻击料理在的话就赶紧吃了，时间凝滞然后射眼使巨人倒下过去近战，巨人起身后远离，重复此流程便可击败它。它身上有一把骑士剑和骑士弓可以在它坐地时拿下。"},{"type":"title","content":"第13层"},{"type":"text","content":"拔出大师剑完成初始试炼。"}]},{"name":"switch游戏如何使用amiibo","content":[{"type":"title","content":"switch游戏如何使用amiibo"},{"type":"text","content":"amiibo是任天堂游戏的一个特色功能，需要购买实体道具和游戏机互动才可以使用，通常官方的游戏周边都有一个nfc芯片，在游戏中打开amiibo功能后，把游戏周边的nfc区域靠近游戏手柄的感应区域即可使用。"},{"type":"text","content":"在购买amiibo实体道具后，我们需要先打开游戏的系统界面。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://pics3.baidu.com/feed/a1ec08fa513d2697204dcb088d1a59f14216d832.jpeg@f_auto?token=8187f64446cf024f1ccf749a896f18d5"},{"type":"text","content":"界面第一个就是amiibo，一般默认关掉的, 点击使用amiibo即可。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://pics4.baidu.com/feed/060828381f30e924a9a6ec9c96e9850c1c95f70d.jpeg@f_auto?token=fae4833cb5911203c91540c2a8094e60"},{"type":"image","content":"https://pics3.baidu.com/feed/cdbf6c81800a19d8df53389fe61b6981a41e46c0.jpeg@f_auto?token=9c11145fda7a5a2cbb5aa475ef1104de"},{"type":"text","content":"之后在希卡之石的功能界面的最后一格就可以找到amiibo图标，选中后对着空地就可以出现光圈。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://pics2.baidu.com/feed/9922720e0cf3d7ca3b2a37b32bfe55036963a907.jpeg@f_auto?token=90491142ae3e5f866be89a8395ae7190"},{"type":"text","content":"此时使用amiibo的实体道具，靠近右侧手柄的感应区域即可使用。成功后会掉落一个宝箱有几率获得amiibo的专属装备和武器，每个amiibo道具一天可以使用一次。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://pics1.baidu.com/feed/ca1349540923dd54ad6f49e930e858d49d824804.jpeg@f_auto?token=4e7546b1e04b66ce7f1c4f7b935f7636"},{"type":"text","content":"以上就是塞尔达传说使用amiibo的流程方法，其他支持使用的游戏操作都类似"}]},{"name":"PC和安卓版Switch游戏及模拟器资源","icon":"cuIcon-video text-red","content":[{"type":"title","content":"PC和安卓版Switch游戏及模拟器资源"},{"type":"video","error":true,"content":"export/UzFfAgtgekIEAQAAAAAAAo8o6WIuBgAAAAstQy6ubaLX4KHWvLEZgBPElKJYDSNaScGKzNPgMJotb50wdleAPNxAuIvGIbSR"},{"type":"text","content":"关注公众号 \n UFO百宝箱 （长按关注）"},{"type":"image","show":true,"content":"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/1362796/1729000382122-009adb2c-f7a5-45ef-9891-2870ea679fa9.png"},{"type":"text","content":"发送消息“塞尔达”获取最新Switch游戏和模拟器（PC版和安卓版，NS通用）"},{"type":"text","content":"后续会持续更新更多资源"}]},{"name":"获取光之弓的方法","content":[{"type":"title","content":"卡光之弓攻略"},{"type":"text","content":"1.第一种方法：在剧情任务的过程中，挑战魔兽盖侬BOSS时，会获得塞尔达公主托付的限时光之弓。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://gp-dev.cdn.bcebos.com/dump/16818169548560?x-bce-process=image/quality,Q_80"},{"type":"text","content":"2.第二种方法：通过入手并刷取amiibo玩具，可以打开宝箱获得永久的特典武器，黄昏光之弓"},{"type":"image","content":"https://gp-dev.cdn.bcebos.com/dump/16818169548591?x-bce-process=image/quality,Q_80"},{"type":"text","content":"3.第三种方法：在剧情中拿到限时光之弓后，骑马朝反方向跑，通过贴着光墙骑行并跳下马的动作，来触发卡出光墙的BUG，然后传送回“沃托里村”，保存并读档后，就可以拿到永久光之弓了"},{"type":"image","content":"https://gp-dev.cdn.bcebos.com/dump/16818169548592?x-bce-process=image/quality,Q_80"}]},{"name":"怪物商店位置","content":[{"type":"title","content":"怪物商店的位置很多玩家不知道在哪里，需要的时候只能到处寻找非常浪费时间"},{"type":"text","content":"一共7处地方 ，几乎是每个村子都有了。"},{"type":"text","content":"最开始的位置在骷髅池塘，当然这里什么也买不了，只能用于激活。"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2020/11/20201119_msl_535_03/image001_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"1.利特村正北"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2020/11/20201119_msl_535_03/image002_S.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2020/11/20201119_msl_535_03/image003_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"2.格鲁德小镇西北"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2020/11/20201119_msl_535_03/image004_S.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2020/11/20201119_msl_535_03/image005_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"3.卡卡利特村"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2020/11/20201119_msl_535_03/image006_S.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2020/11/20201119_msl_535_03/image007_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"4.沃托里村南面"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2020/11/20201119_msl_535_03/image008_S.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2020/11/20201119_msl_535_03/image009_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"5.哈特诺村"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2020/11/20201119_msl_535_03/image010_S.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2020/11/20201119_msl_535_03/image011_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"6.卓拉领地"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2020/11/20201119_msl_535_03/image012_S.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2020/11/20201119_msl_535_03/image013_S.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"7.一始村下面"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2020/11/20201119_msl_535_03/image014_S.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2020/11/20201119_msl_535_03/image015_S.jpg"}]},{"name":"初期快速挣钱方法之1.做厨师，卖料理","content":[{"type":"title","content":"方法一：做厨师，卖料理"},{"type":"text","content":"达成条件：简单"},{"type":"text","content":"挣钱效率：低"},{"type":"text","content":"推荐等级：★★"},{"type":"text","content":"在海拉尔大陆上有相当多的动植物供你采集制作食物或药水，这些食物和药水都可以拿去卖钱，不过我们这里竟然讲究挣钱，那肯定要选性价比最高的了。"},{"type":"text","content":"我们可以在各种哺乳类动物的生上猎到生肉，各种鸟类身上猎到鸟肉，这两种食材也是相对比较容易就能得到的食材。而混合五个这两种食材就可以制作烤肉串，这个烤肉串拿到商店卖可以得到120卢比，"},{"type":"text","content":"在前期你制作的普通食物中是卖的最好的一种，假设五支弓箭是20卢比的话，就是净利率100卢比"},{"type":"image","content":"https://img1.ali213.net/glpic/2017/03/13/584_201703131008401000.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"不过这个方法的话需要你去各地打猎，如果你不是特别擅长使用弓箭，或是没有找到一个比较好的打猎地点的话，还是不推荐这种方法，耗时也耗力，效率不高。"}]},{"name":"初期快速挣钱方法之2.玩游戏，捉迷藏","content":[{"type":"title","content":"方法二：玩游戏，捉迷藏"},{"type":"text","content":"达成条件：简单"},{"type":"text","content":"挣钱效率：低"},{"type":"text","content":"推荐等级：★★☆"},{"type":"text","content":"在新手村kakariko，你可以遇见一个叫做cottla的小孩，她会要求你跟她玩游戏"},{"type":"text","content":"这个游戏是有两种，分别是捉迷藏和你追我赶，这里我们选择你追我赶，cottla会在三个地方刷新出来，我们每次只要往正确的方向走就可以很快追上她，"},{"type":"text","content":"追上她之后她会给我们一个奖励，这个奖励有可能是琥珀(30卢比)，也有可能是岩盐(2卢比)，二者的概率一半一半"},{"type":"text","content":"玩一次游戏大概20秒左右。如果欧气十足的话，是可以很快刷到很多琥珀然后卖出去换钱，当然琥珀也有升级装备的作用，所以如何取舍就看你们自身，下图给出这个小孩分别会出现的几个地方的抓捕办法"},{"type":"text","content":"第1个地点，绕路上去既可以迎面抓到她"},{"type":"image","content":"https://img1.ali213.net/glpic/2017/03/13/584_20170313100841638.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第2个地点，直接冲上前抓住她"},{"type":"image","content":"https://img1.ali213.net/glpic/2017/03/13/584_20170313100842281.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"第3个地点，一样冲上前抓住她"},{"type":"image","content":"https://img1.ali213.net/glpic/2017/03/13/584_20170313100843169.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"这种方法刷到物品的概率虽然快，但同时也存在脸黑脸白的差别，琥珀呢也是一个只能卖30，即使脸特别欧每次都拿，拿到10个也需要3分钟左右的时间，结果却也只是300卢比的价格，效率还是偏低，只推荐给那些不愿意跑路脸又特别欧的人。"}]},{"name":"初期快速挣钱方法之3.赌箱子","content":[{"type":"title","content":"方法三：赌箱子"},{"type":"text","content":"达成条件：中等"},{"type":"text","content":"挣钱效率：低"},{"type":"text","content":"推荐等级：★★★"},{"type":"text","content":"这一个方法需要我们跑路到一个叫做Lureilin的村子，地点大概在如下地图的位置"},{"type":"image","content":"https://img1.ali213.net/glpic/2017/03/13/584_20170313100844336.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"过来之后，可以先攻略该村子附近的神庙开启快速传送。然后去村中一个比较大的房子寻找一个叫做Clonye的人，他会跟我们玩一个赌博的游戏"},{"type":"text","content":"我们可以押10~100元的卢比，然后去开他房子中三个箱子中的一个，如果开对了就会有非常可观的奖励。"},{"type":"text","content":"一般来说，我们需要先保存一下，然后直接压100卢比，如果开对的话是会有300卢比的奖励，纯收益也就是200卢比。脸欧的话这种方法进钱很快，连续10把都猜对，不到5分钟的时间赢2000卢比"},{"type":"image","content":"https://img1.ali213.net/glpic/2017/03/13/584_20170313100845335.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://img1.ali213.net/glpic/2017/03/13/584_20170313100846353.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"这一种办法也是需要考察人品，那些脸黑的同志还是放弃这种办法吧"}]},{"name":"初期快速挣钱方法之4.滚雪球","icon":"cuIcon-light text-red","content":[{"type":"title","content":"方法四：滚雪球"},{"type":"text","content":"达成条件：跑路较远"},{"type":"text","content":"挣钱效率：快"},{"type":"text","content":"推荐等级：★★★★★"},{"type":"text","content":"前期挣钱最快的一种方法，掌握好了诀窍使用这种方法简直一本万利，效率奇高，关键是还不看脸，20分钟刷出15000的卢比。这个方法唯一的缺点就是跑路较远，要跑到一个非常远的高塔处，不过到了之后你就可以同步地图开启快速传送点，再过来就很简单了。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://img1.ali213.net/glpic/2017/03/13/584_2017031310084785.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"赶路到达hebra tower后，利用火箭融化周围的一块冰块儿就可以爬上去了，到达塔顶后往下看会看到一个小屋，我们降落在一个小屋前会有一个老爷爷在滚雪球，他会问我们要不要玩一个滚雪球的游戏，是要把雪球抛掷出去击打下面的木头块儿，类似于保龄球的一种游戏。"},{"type":"text","content":"如果愿意玩的话是需要20的卢比来挑战，总共两次机会，一次性把所有木块都打倒的话爷爷是会给我们300卢比的奖励，如果花了两次打倒所有木块是只有100卢比，如果没有全部击倒就只有20~90卢比的奖励。"},{"type":"image","content":"https://img1.ali213.net/glpic/2017/03/13/584_20170313100847189.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://img1.ali213.net/glpic/2017/03/13/584_20170313100848477.jpg"},{"type":"text","content":"掌握了方法的话是能百分百击倒所有木块的。在我们抛掷地点的附近有一个突出来的小岩石，我们站在岩石的右手边，把视角对准山崖下右侧的第一棵树 ，然后再投掷雪球，这样的话雪球会百分百滚向中间的雪道进而击倒所有的木块的。"},{"type":"text","content":"如果有尝试不得要领的话可以多试几次，仔细观察一下所在的方位和视角，熟练后保证成功率90%以上，每次纯收益有280卢比，一把时间30秒左右，最多一分钟，简直效率，强烈推荐使用此办法!"},{"type":"image","content":"https://img1.ali213.net/glpic/2017/03/13/584_20170313100925872.jpg"},{"type":"image","content":"https://img1.ali213.net/glpic/2017/03/13/584_20170313100926675.jpg"}]}]}]